NK034(ngi)004:0: gser yig can rdo rje 'chang gis gsungs pa mchod
NK034(ngi)004:1: 'os rang bzhin gyi tshig dus gnad nges pa bzhugs
NK034(ngi)004:2: so rgya gar skad du bud+d+ha sarba pu tra e
NK034(ngi)004:3: ka tan tra u pa d+he sha n+aa mah bod
NK034(ngi)004:4: skad du / sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sras gcig
NK034(ngi)004:5: gi rgyud kyi man ngag ces bya ba thog ma'i
NK034(ngi)004:6: mgon po 'od mi 'gyur ba la phyag 'tshal lo
NK034(ngi)004:7: de nas rdo rje 'chang gis ni thugs kyi dkyil
NK034(ngi)004:8: 'khor sgo phye nas tshig gi rgyal po 'di dag
NK034(ngi)004:9: kun rdo rje'i mgur du rab dril te ljags kyi
NK034(ngi)004:10: dbang po la bkram nas tshems ni bzhi bcu'i bar
NK034(ngi)004:11: nas ni gsang chen dam pa'i tshig 'di kun ma
NK034(ngi)004:12: brjod 'phros pa'i tshul gyis gsungs kyee snang ba'i rgyal
NK034(ngi)004:13: po a la la sangs rgyas rnams kyi sras gcig
NK034(ngi)004:14: po bstan pa'i sa bon yang zhun gdung don dam
NK034(ngi)004:15: rgyal po'i rtags chen po snying po sprul pa'i sku
NK034(ngi)004:16: 'di ni klog dang 'dzin dang bcang ba'i thabs 'di
NK034(ngi)004:17: nyid rim pa ji lta bar snying po gsang ba
NK034(ngi)004:18: nga yis kyang spro bar bya'o gsang ba'i bdag rnal
NK034(ngi)004:19: 'byor skal dang su ldan pa 'di ni snang bar
NK034(ngi)004:20: yang dag go de yi sangs rgyas sras po 'di
NK034(ngi)004:21: sangs rgyas bden pa mthong ba des sprul pa'i sku
NK034(ngi)004:22: ni 'di ltar bcang bdag gi spyi bo'i gtsug gam
NK034(ngi)004:23: ni mchan khung ngam ni mgul du'o rang byung chen
NK034(ngi)004:24: po'i yi ge rnams rin chen gser gyis bris nas
NK034(ngi)004:25: ni glegs bam sor ni bzhi pa'i tshad sna tshogs
NK034(ngi)004:26: dar gyis gril nas kyang rang gi spyi bor bzung
NK034(ngi)004:27: na yang 'di la sprul pa'i yon tan thob mchan
NK034(ngi)004:28: khung g.yon du bcangs pa yi 'di yang de dang
NK034(ngi)004:29: mnyam pa yin 'di nyid mgul du btags nas ni
NK034(ngi)004:30: rgyun du gus par byed pa la 'di yang sprul
NK034(ngi)004:31: sku'i yon tan thob rang byung yi ge 'di dag
NK034(ngi)004:32: la glegs bam de ltar bzung nas ni 'di ltar
NK034(ngi)004:33: mchod pa yang dag bya gal te sa g.yos byung
NK034(ngi)004:34: tshe na 'di nyid lan drug lan bdun nam yang
NK034(ngi)004:35: na lan ni lnga'am gsum rdo rje'i lce yis bklag
NK034(ngi)004:36: par bya tshogs ni rnal 'byor lo yi grangs 'di
NK034(ngi)004:37: yis dus su rab tu btang dam tshig mchog ldan
NK034(ngi)004:38: rnal 'byor pas tshogs kyi mchod pa de bzhin bya
NK034(ngi)004:39: bklag pa 'byung ba byer dus su tshogs ni snyoms
NK034(ngi)004:40: pa'i dus na bya ston mo de bzhin 'khrugs pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:41: dus rnal 'byor pa ni zug pa yi dus na
NK034(ngi)004:42: so so'i gnas nas 'bod 'di ltar 'byung ba'i khyad
NK034(ngi)004:43: par las rnal 'byor de ni thar lam du yang
NK034(ngi)004:44: dag nges par 'jug pa yi rdo rje 'chang ba
NK034(ngi)004:45: rnams dang ni skal pa yang dag mnyam pa'o sgra
NK034(ngi)004:46: ni byung ba'i dus na yang lan ni drug gam
NK034(ngi)004:47: bdun dang lngar pad ma yi ni lce yis ni
NK034(ngi)004:48: skal dang ldan pas bklag par bya 'di dus lha
NK034(ngi)004:49: la mchod par 'bul dge slong tshul khrims ldan pa
NK034(ngi)004:50: la chos dang mthun pa'i ston mo bya bklag pa
NK034(ngi)004:51: byed pa'i dus na yin mchod pa de bzhin snyoms
NK034(ngi)004:52: pa la dge slong zug pa'i dus na 'bod ston
NK034(ngi)004:53: mo 'khrugs pa'i dus na bya 'di ltar su yis
NK034(ngi)004:54: byas pa de 'di yang sprul pa'i sku dang mnyam
NK034(ngi)004:55: 'od kyi snang ba byung ba'i tshe lan lnga gsum
NK034(ngi)004:56: mam lan gcig tu dung gi lce yis bklag par
NK034(ngi)004:57: bya 'di dus rlung ni sgom par bya rnal 'byor
NK034(ngi)004:58: ma ni dam tshig can dagu'am bcu gcig man chod
NK034(ngi)004:59: la bza' btung rtsub pa'i ston mo bya bklag pa
NK034(ngi)004:60: snyoms pa'i dus na yin rlung ni byer ba'i dus
NK034(ngi)004:61: na yin rnal 'byor la ni snyoms pa la ston
NK034(ngi)004:62: mo 'khrugs pa'i dus na'o 'di ltar byas pa'i rnal
NK034(ngi)004:63: 'byor pa sprul pa'i sku dang yang mnyam mo sad
NK034(ngi)004:64: kyis rgyal khams khyab pa'i tshe ral gri'i lce yis
NK034(ngi)004:65: 'di brjod na sangs rgyas yon tan 'di yis thob
NK034(ngi)004:66: 'di dus sgra yi mchod pa bya rnal 'byor lnga'am
NK034(ngi)004:67: bco lnga la byin brlabs gtor ma lan bdun btang
NK034(ngi)004:68: bklag pa zug pa'i dus na yin mchod pa snyoms
NK034(ngi)004:69: pa'i tshe na'o byer ba la ni rnal 'byor 'bod
NK034(ngi)004:70: 'khrugs pa'i tshe na ston mo btang 'di ltar su
NK034(ngi)004:71: yis byas pa la sprul pa sku yi yon tan
NK034(ngi)004:72: thob rims dang yams nad byung ba'i tshe dgu dang
NK034(ngi)004:73: bcu gcig bcu dgur ni lcags kyu'i lce yis brjod
NK034(ngi)004:74: bar bya 'di dus rnam par mi rtog bsgom byis
NK034(ngi)004:75: pa dagu'am bco brgyad la ston mo bya bar rab
NK034(ngi)004:76: tu basngagasa bklag pa 'khrugs pa'i dus na yin sgom
NK034(ngi)004:77: pa snyoms pa'i dus na'o byis pa byer ba'i dus
NK034(ngi)004:78: su 'bod ston mo zug pa nyid la bya de
NK034(ngi)004:79: ltar byas pa'i skyes mchog ni 'di la sprul pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:80: yon tan thob nyi zla gza' yis zin pa'i tshe
NK034(ngi)004:81: 'di ni lan lnga drug gam dgu 'khor lo'i lce
NK034(ngi)004:82: yis yang brjod na 'di yang sprul pa'i sku dang
NK034(ngi)004:83: mnyam 'di dus srog 'don dge ba bya dud 'gro'i
NK034(ngi)004:84: rigs la ston mo btang bklag pa bye ba'i dus
NK034(ngi)004:85: na yin srog 'don snyoms pa nyid la'o dud 'gro
NK034(ngi)004:86: zug pa'i dus na yin ston mo 'khrugs pa'i dus
NK034(ngi)004:87: na bya de ltar ston mo sus byas pa sprul
NK034(ngi)004:88: pa sku yi yon tan thob mu ge dag ni
NK034(ngi)004:89: byung ba'i tshe kha t+w+aam lce yis rab brjod na
NK034(ngi)004:90: 'dis kyang sprul sku 'dzin pa yin lan ni lnga'am
NK034(ngi)004:91: gsum gnyis yin 'di dus dri yi macha da pa
NK034(ngi)004:92: bya shan pa'am ni mu stegs la ston mo bya
NK034(ngi)004:93: bar rab tu bzang bklag pa byer ba'i dus na
NK034(ngi)004:94: yin mchod pa snyoms pa nyid la bya sdig can
NK034(ngi)004:95: 'khrugs pa nyid la 'bod ston mo de bzhin zug
NK034(ngi)004:96: pa la'o 'dis kyang sprul sku'i sa bon 'jog rgyal
NK034(ngi)004:97: khams phyugs nad byung ba'i dus rang byung chen po'i
NK034(ngi)004:98: yi ge 'di lan brgyad dang ni bcu drug tu
NK034(ngi)004:99: rtse gsum lce yis 'di brjod do 'di dus mar
NK034(ngi)004:100: me'i mchod pa bya dgra bcom pa ni bdun la
NK034(ngi)004:101: yang ston mo bya bar rab tu basngagasa bklag pa
NK034(ngi)004:102: zug pa nyid la yin mchod par byer ba nyid
NK034(ngi)004:103: la bya dgra bcom snyoms pa'i dus na 'bod 'khrugs
NK034(ngi)004:104: pa la ni ston mo bya de ltar byas pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:105: skyes bu la sprul pa'i sa bon nges par 'jog
NK034(ngi)004:106: 'di la the tshom byar mi rung nges gsang 'bras
NK034(ngi)004:107: bu dam pa'o +amo dang yang dag su ldan pa
NK034(ngi)004:108: sangs rgyas rnams kyi sku la sbyor h+aum dang yang
NK034(ngi)004:109: dag su ldan pa 'di ni thugs ka de bzhin
NK034(ngi)004:110: no +aam dang yang dag su ldan pa gsung la
NK034(ngi)004:111: yang dag 'di yis reg de phyir ngag gi spyod
NK034(ngi)004:112: pa gces gang gis seng ge byas pa na 'di
NK034(ngi)004:113: la nad dang 'jigs pa bral glang po su yis
NK034(ngi)004:114: byas pa la 'di la srog med dbugs kyang med
NK034(ngi)004:115: drang srong gang gis byas pa la mi rtog las
NK034(ngi)004:116: byung zer zug snyoms 'di ltar lus kyi bya byed
NK034(ngi)004:117: gces smig rgyu rang yul sus shes pa 'di la
NK034(ngi)004:118: rtag med chad pa med dran bsam bral ba sus
NK034(ngi)004:119: shes pa 'di la 'ong med 'gro ba med cer
NK034(ngi)004:120: mthong rang ngo sus shes pa 'di la 'khor dang
NK034(ngi)004:121: myang 'das med 'di ltar sems kyi dngos po gces
NK034(ngi)004:122: e ma rang byung cheen po'i yi ge 'di rab
NK034(ngi)004:123: tu ngo mtshar che bas na ha ha 'di ltar
NK034(ngi)004:124: sus kyang ma byas pa rang byung kun gyi thog
NK034(ngi)004:125: mar byung a la la ho sprul pa'i sku 'di
NK034(ngi)004:126: la byed pa'i rkyen med pas tha ma 'jigs pa
NK034(ngi)004:127: kun dang bral 'byung bas cung zad gnod pa med
NK034(ngi)004:128: 'di ni nam mkha' 'bar bar nges sangs rgyas sprul
NK034(ngi)004:129: pa yin pa na 'di la bshad cing sgom pa
NK034(ngi)004:130: med 'di bral bems po sgom par snang de phyir
NK034(ngi)004:131: 'di dang 'phrad par yang rab tu dka' zhing snang
NK034(ngi)004:132: ba min des na 'di dang gang phrad pa sangs
NK034(ngi)004:133: rgyas 'bras bu thob pa la the tshom dgos pa
NK034(ngi)004:134: ma yin no e ma 'jig rten gang zhig na
NK034(ngi)004:135: sangs rgyas 'bras bu sus thob tshe de tshe rang
NK034(ngi)004:136: byung chen po 'di 'phar zhing rang 'od lnga po
NK034(ngi)004:137: 'byung de tshe lan gsum bklag par bya de yang
NK034(ngi)004:138: de dang mnyam par 'gyur 'di ni bcangs pa tsam
NK034(ngi)004:139: gyi kyang sangs rgyas nyid du 'gyur ba la the
NK034(ngi)004:140: tshom za ba ci zhig dgos gal te byol song
NK034(ngi)004:141: mgul du 'di btags na de nyid grol bas na
NK034(ngi)004:142: 'gro ba mi rnams smos ci dgos e ma rang
NK034(ngi)004:143: byung yi ge 'di sems can gzhan gyi don byed
NK034(ngi)004:144: na tshe 'das de yi spyi bo'am mgul du 'di
NK034(ngi)004:145: btags bsregs na ni de nyid grol bar smos ci
NK034(ngi)004:146: dgos mtshams med lnga po spyad pa yang nyan thos
NK034(ngi)004:147: rnams dang skal ba mnyam lung du ma bstan skye
NK034(ngi)004:148: bo rnams byang chub sems dpa'i sa dang mnyam yid
NK034(ngi)004:149: dpyod 'dzin pa'i grub mtha' yang rdo rje 'chang dang
NK034(ngi)004:150: mnyam par nges 'di dang phrad pa'i skal ba can
NK034(ngi)004:151: snying 'dra sems kyi bu gcig la rig pa dngos
NK034(ngi)004:152: kyi rtags yod pas bklag cing bsreg par bya mi
NK034(ngi)004:153: dgos phrad pa tsam gyis 'grub pa yin byer zug
NK034(ngi)004:154: la sogs bshad mi dgos de yi rtags rnams 'byung
NK034(ngi)004:155: ba ni byol song me 'od dkar gsal la dud
NK034(ngi)004:156: pa sngon po shar phyogs su rus pa'i 'od kyang
NK034(ngi)004:157: dmar gsal yin gser gyi yig 'bru ma zhig bar
NK034(ngi)004:158: de yi rus pa nyid la 'byar 'di nas zla
NK034(ngi)004:159: ba bcu gsum na sa rnams nges par g.yo ba
NK034(ngi)004:160: yin de dus 'od kyang mog mog po snang ba
NK034(ngi)004:161: nges par 'gyur ba yin sdig can me mdog ser
NK034(ngi)004:162: la gsal dud pa nub phyogs kha dog dkar rus
NK034(ngi)004:163: pa'i mdog ni sngo nag la yi ge zhig ste
NK034(ngi)004:164: thig ler snang 'di nas zla ba dgu na yang
NK034(ngi)004:165: sgra ni shar gyi phyogs su 'byung 'di la 'od
NK034(ngi)004:166: ni mer mer po 'di don nges par yang dag
NK034(ngi)004:167: go yid dpyod grub pa'i mtha' 'dzin pa'i me mdog
NK034(ngi)004:168: dkar gsal g.yos pa med dud pa sngon po gyen
NK034(ngi)004:169: 'greng 'byung rus mdog dkar po thig le can yi
NK034(ngi)004:170: ge 'di nyid ma zhig par kha dog dkar po
NK034(ngi)004:171: 'od dang ldan skabs skabs rus pa'i dkyil na snang
NK034(ngi)004:172: 'di la sku dang gdung yang 'byung 'di nas zhag
NK034(ngi)004:173: ni gsum na yang sgra ni shar gyi phyogs nas
NK034(ngi)004:174: 'ong 'od ni nub kyi phyogs su snang 'di ni
NK034(ngi)004:175: nges par sprul pa yi sku yi 'bras bu rnyed
NK034(ngi)004:176: pa yin kye ma snang bdag rang bzhin sprul pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:177: sku de yi phyi nang gsang tshig ni thun mong
NK034(ngi)004:178: nyid du phrad pa min rigs ldan skyes bu skal
NK034(ngi)004:179: chen po 'ga' la 'di nyid snang ba las kun
NK034(ngi)004:180: gyis mthong ba ma yin no rang byung yi ge
NK034(ngi)004:181: 'di med par skyes bu nyid ni gang su rung
NK034(ngi)004:182: sems can don nyid byed 'dod kyang sems can don
NK034(ngi)004:183: ni nus pa min yang dag lam ni mthong ba
NK034(ngi)004:184: min yang dag lam ni mthong srid kyang nyan thos
NK034(ngi)004:185: rnams dang khyad ci yod kun gyi spyod yul ma
NK034(ngi)004:186: yin no gal te 'di nyid phrad na yang 'di
NK034(ngi)004:187: ni nges pa'i sprul pas na sgrib byed nyid dang
NK034(ngi)004:188: ma bral bas 'di la the tshom skye bar 'gyur
NK034(ngi)004:189: des na 'di nyid rnam spangs pas 'bras bu gtan
NK034(ngi)004:190: nas brlag pa yin skal pa mchog rab ldan pa
NK034(ngi)004:191: kun the tshom skye bar ga la srid de yis
NK034(ngi)004:192: 'di nyid gsang chen du yang dag par ni 'gyur
NK034(ngi)004:193: ba'o gal te 'di nyid snang ba'i mis 'di nyid
NK034(ngi)004:194: yod par su gzhan la smra bar byed pa'i mi
NK034(ngi)004:195: de yi rang gi 'bras bu rang brlag tu 'di
NK034(ngi)004:196: yis byed pa kho na yin de yi phyir na
NK034(ngi)004:197: rang byung gi yi ge 'di nyid yod pa'i mis
NK034(ngi)004:198: tshig zur tsam yang smra mi bya gsang ba las
NK034(ngi)004:199: ni dngos grub 'byung ma gsang mchog dang thun mong
NK034(ngi)004:200: gi dngos grub de yis spangs pa yin gsang ste
NK034(ngi)004:201: lus la yang dag bcang 'di dang bral bar ma
NK034(ngi)004:202: byas na nam zhig 'chi ba'i dus kyi tshe 'di
NK034(ngi)004:203: nyid lus la gnas pa la rigs drug skye ba
NK034(ngi)004:204: rnam bzhi yi grong khyer du ni 'jug mi srid
NK034(ngi)004:205: de yi phyir na 'di nyid dang 'gro dang nyal
NK034(ngi)004:206: dang 'dug pa dang de bzhin za dang 'chag pa
NK034(ngi)004:207: dang phyag dang skor ba la sogs dang 'dud pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:208: lag pa gar nyid dang skyugs dang khrus byed phyi
NK034(ngi)004:209: sa 'dor de bzhin smra dang sngags zlos dang yi
NK034(ngi)004:210: ge klog dang mchod bshags dang ji ltar smra ba
NK034(ngi)004:211: la sogs dang bsam pa ji snyed g.yo ba dang
NK034(ngi)004:212: ji ltar sna tshogs spyod byed kyang 'di dang 'bral
NK034(ngi)004:213: bar mi bya'o 'di ni ris med sprul pa'i sku
NK034(ngi)004:214: rang gzhan don rnams rdzogs par byed byol song rigs
NK034(ngi)004:215: sam bud med dang skye ba dman pa'i sems can
NK034(ngi)004:216: yang 'di dang bral bar ma byas na nges par
NK034(ngi)004:217: 'bras bu thob pas na bral ba'i bar mtshams ma
NK034(ngi)004:218: zhugs pa 'di la rab tu gces pa yin de
NK034(ngi)004:219: bzhin drod dang ma bral bar rgyun du lus la
NK034(ngi)004:220: bcang bar bya gal te dus tshod byung ba'i tshe
NK034(ngi)004:221: 'di nyid klog par yang dag go 'di nyid bcangs
NK034(ngi)004:222: pas nges par 'grub 'chang ba'i gsang tshig yi ge
NK034(ngi)004:223: ni dran pa kun gyi thog ma yi dbang po
NK034(ngi)004:224: zhen pa bzlog pa nas rab tu dkon tshig yan
NK034(ngi)004:225: chad la gser ram bee d+aur+ya yis bri mgul lam
NK034(ngi)004:226: spyi bor btags pas 'grub mngon rdzogs rgyal por sangs
NK034(ngi)004:227: rgyas thob ces rdo rje 'chang gi gsungs pa la
NK034(ngi)004:228: mngon par bstod de rjes su yi rang ngo mchod
NK034(ngi)004:229: 'os rang bzhin gyi dam tshig chen po'i tshig shin
NK034(ngi)004:230: tu gsang na nges par 'grub pa'i bka' gsang gnyan
NK034(ngi)004:231: po rdzogs pa chen po gser gyi snying po nyi
NK034(ngi)004:232: ma rab tu snang byed kyi man ngag dus gnad
NK034(ngi)004:233: nges pa rdzogs so s+aa m+aa y+aa rgya rgya rgya
NK034(ngi)004:234: sangs rgyas kyi 'das rjes gsum bzhugs so rgya gar
NK034(ngi)004:235: skad du bud d+ha d+he ka ra ye d+hu n+aa
NK034(ngi)004:236: mah bod skad du sangs rgyas kyi zhal chems dang
NK034(ngi)004:237: po zhes bya ba yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs
NK034(ngi)004:238: rgyas drug pa rdo rje 'chang la phyag 'tshal lo
NK034(ngi)004:239: kye ma kye ma rigs kyi bu rnams gsang sngags
NK034(ngi)004:240: kyi gnad thams cad gcig tu dril nas nyams su
NK034(ngi)004:241: long zhig lus ngag yid kyi sngon 'gro ni mi
NK034(ngi)004:242: rtag snying rje byang sems sbyang lus 'di ma rig
NK034(ngi)004:243: rgyud bskyed phyir rigs drug sa bon nyid du gnad
NK034(ngi)004:244: rig pa sku gsum dngos yin phyir sku gsum yi
NK034(ngi)004:245: ge gsum du shar yi ge'i rtsal sbyang ru shan
NK034(ngi)004:246: dbye de nas rnal du dbab pa'i phyir nyan thos
NK034(ngi)004:247: byang sems khro bo yi lta stangs nyid kyis sor
NK034(ngi)004:248: yang gzhug gnas brtan grol ba'i gdeng thob nas phyi
NK034(ngi)004:249: nang bya ba kun btang ste glang seng drang srong
NK034(ngi)004:250: 'dug stangs bca' ngag ni smra ba rgyun bcad la
NK034(ngi)004:251: sems ni smin phrag mkha' la gtad sgo yul rlung
NK034(ngi)004:252: gi gnad bstun pas yul la ye shes mngon du
NK034(ngi)004:253: snang mngon sum gnad las 'bral mi bya mi 'gul
NK034(ngi)004:254: gsum la gzhi bcas pas snang ba bzhi yi drod
NK034(ngi)004:255: rnyed nas sdod pa gsum gyi tshad zin te thob
NK034(ngi)004:256: pa gsum gyi gzer thebs nas khams gsum dag tu
NK034(ngi)004:257: ldog re skan mya ngan 'da' bar the tshom med
NK034(ngi)004:258: ces sum cu rtsa gsum gyi lho phyogs sman 'tsho
NK034(ngi)004:259: byed gzhon nu'i ldum rar rdo rje 'chang chen po
NK034(ngi)004:260: yongs su mya ngan 'da' ba'i tshul bstan pa'i tshe
NK034(ngi)004:261: dga' rab rdo rje sa la 'gyel zhing gdung ba'i
NK034(ngi)004:262: smre sngags phyung ba kye ma kyi hud kye ma
NK034(ngi)004:263: klong ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub na 'jig rten
NK034(ngi)004:264: mun pa gang gis sel zhes brjod de brgyal sangs
NK034(ngi)004:265: ba dang 'od phung gi nang nas phyag g.yas pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:266: gru mo man chad phyung nas rin po che shel
NK034(ngi)004:267: gyi za ma tog sen gang ba zhig phyag g.yas
NK034(ngi)004:268: pa'i mthil du babs te de zhal phye bas rin
NK034(ngi)004:269: po che mthing ka la bee d+aur+ya bzhu ba'i khu
NK034(ngi)004:270: bas bris pa babs pas dga' rab rdo rje rtogs
NK034(ngi)004:271: pa'i gdeng dang ldan par gyur to sa ma y+aa
NK034(ngi)004:272: rgya gar skad du bud d+ha d+he ka ra ma
NK034(ngi)004:273: du n+aa mah bod skad du sangs rgyas kyi 'das
NK034(ngi)004:274: rjes gnyis pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)004:275: dbang po'i stobs kyis rnam par gnon pa nyid la
NK034(ngi)004:276: phyag 'tshal lo nges par sangs rgyas thob 'dod na
NK034(ngi)004:277: sngon du 'gro la rtsal nyid sbyang lus dang ngag
NK034(ngi)004:278: dang yid gsum po ru shan legs par ma phyed
NK034(ngi)004:279: na khams gsum nyid las mi bsgrod pas sngon du
NK034(ngi)004:280: 'gro ba dag la bslab sngon 'gro'i gnad la mkhas
NK034(ngi)004:281: gyur na mchog thun dgongs pa la mkhas 'gyur dben
NK034(ngi)004:282: pa'i gnas su gcig pur 'dug lus kyi sngon 'gro
NK034(ngi)004:283: bya ba'i phyir rigs drug spyod pa sna tshogs spyad
NK034(ngi)004:284: dkon mchog gsum gyi spyod pa bya skyil krung mthil
NK034(ngi)004:285: sprad drang por bsrang spyi bor thal mo sbyar bar
NK034(ngi)004:286: bya de ltar lus kyis sus byas pa lus de
NK034(ngi)004:287: mi ldog bar chad zhi zhen pa ldog cing sgrib
NK034(ngi)004:288: pa 'dag lus de sprul pa'i skur grol nas sangs
NK034(ngi)004:289: rgyas sku dang gnyis su med lhag med nyid du
NK034(ngi)004:290: 'gyur ba'o ngag gi sngon 'gro bya ba'i phyir rigs
NK034(ngi)004:291: drug sgra skad sna tshogs brjod zhi khro'i sgra dang
NK034(ngi)004:292: 'byung ba'i sgra rnam pa sna tshogs nyid la spyad
NK034(ngi)004:293: rgyas gdab gnad la zhag gsum bya rtsal sbyang gnyen
NK034(ngi)004:294: btsal lam du gzhug de ltar ngag gis sus byas
NK034(ngi)004:295: pa zhen log ngag gi sgrib pa dag mi ldog
NK034(ngi)004:296: gnyis med longs skur grol yid kyi sngon 'gro bya
NK034(ngi)004:297: ba'i phyir rigs drug sdug bsngal blo la blang de
NK034(ngi)004:298: nas sems kyi byung sa btsal ma rnyed chos kyi
NK034(ngi)004:299: sku dang sprad de nas sems kyi gnas sa btsal
NK034(ngi)004:300: ma rnyed longs spyod sku dang sprad de nas sems
NK034(ngi)004:301: kyi 'gro sa btsal ma rnyed sprul pa'i sku dang
NK034(ngi)004:302: sprad de ltar sems kyis sus byas pa zhen log
NK034(ngi)004:303: bar chad zhi ba dang sgrib dag khams gsum ldog
NK034(ngi)004:304: pa med chos kyi skur grol gnyis med 'da' de
NK034(ngi)004:305: nas lus ngag yid gsum po rnal du 'bebs la
NK034(ngi)004:306: mkhas par bya des ni gsum po sor chud nas
NK034(ngi)004:307: nyams len nyid la brtson par 'gyur de ltar sngon
NK034(ngi)004:308: 'gro rdzogs byas nas de dag blo yis bor nas
NK034(ngi)004:309: kyang mngon sum gnad la dbab pa'i phyir lus ngag
NK034(ngi)004:310: yid gsum bya ba spang 'di ni dur khrod chen
NK034(ngi)004:311: po me ri 'bar ba'i shar phyogs d+aak+ki ma sna
NK034(ngi)004:312: tshogs 'du ba'i gnas su yang dag par rdzogs pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:313: sangs rgyas yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul
NK034(ngi)004:314: bstan pa'i tshe dga' rab rdo rje sa la 'gyel
NK034(ngi)004:315: te gdung ba'i smre sngags phyung ba kye ma kyi
NK034(ngi)004:316: hud kye ma klong ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub
NK034(ngi)004:317: na 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel zhes brjod
NK034(ngi)004:318: de brgyal sangs pa dang mdun gyi nam mkhar 'od
NK034(ngi)004:319: phung gi dkyil du phyag g.yas pa'i gru mo man
NK034(ngi)004:320: chad phyung nas bee d+aur+ya zhun ma nyid la rin
NK034(ngi)004:321: po che lnga yi yi ge rang byung du bkod
NK034(ngi)004:322: pa rin po che shel gyi za ma tog dang
NK034(ngi)004:323: bcas pa babs pa byin rlabs chen po mchog gi
NK034(ngi)004:324: yi ge sangs rgyas kyi zhal chems gnyis pa sprul
NK034(ngi)004:325: pa po dga' rab rdo rje bzung ba'i don du
NK034(ngi)004:326: snang bar byas pa mya ngan las 'da' ba thams
NK034(ngi)004:327: cad kyi sna khrid dang 'dra ba bstan pa thams
NK034(ngi)004:328: cad kyi bcud bsdus shing bu gcig par bstan pa'o
NK034(ngi)004:329: sa ma y+aa rgya gar skad du bud d+ha d+he
NK034(ngi)004:330: ka ra ya tri n+aa mah bod skad du sangs
NK034(ngi)004:331: rgyas kyi 'das rjes gsum pa rang grol rdo rje
NK034(ngi)004:332: 'chang la phyag 'tshal lo kye ma kye ma rigs
NK034(ngi)004:333: kyi bu rnams gson cig lus ni mya ngan 'da'
NK034(ngi)004:334: 'dod na sku gsum bzhugs stangs nyid la bslab 'di
NK034(ngi)004:335: ltar su yis byas pa ni dus gsum sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)004:336: thams cad kyi sku yi klong du mya ngan 'da'
NK034(ngi)004:337: ngag ni bslab bya'i rim pa dang gnas pa brtan
NK034(ngi)004:338: zhing la yang bzla de las mi 'da' sus byas
NK034(ngi)004:339: pa dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad kyi gsung gi
NK034(ngi)004:340: klong du mya ngan 'ada'o sems gnas gzigs stangs gsum
NK034(ngi)004:341: gcun te yul gnad nam mkha' rkyen bral la sgo
NK034(ngi)004:342: gnad zlog phab zur gyis lta rlung gnad shin tu
NK034(ngi)004:343: dal la bslab de ltar gnad gsum gzir ba yis
NK034(ngi)004:344: sku gsum rig pa stong par 'char lug rgyud rig
NK034(ngi)004:345: pa btson du bzung mngom sum gnad mthong bzlog pa
NK034(ngi)004:346: med chos nyid mngon sum snang ba yis yid dpyod
NK034(ngi)004:347: 'dzin pa'i lta ba nub gong du 'phel ba'i nyams
NK034(ngi)004:348: snang gis bar dor ye shes mngon du byas rig
NK034(ngi)004:349: pa tshad phebs snang ba yis longs spyod rdzogs pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:350: sku ngos zin chos nyid zad pa'i snang ba yis
NK034(ngi)004:351: rdzogs chen bya bral 'bras bu thob 'di ltar bzhi
NK034(ngi)004:352: la mthar phyin na myang 'das gzhan du btsal mi
NK034(ngi)004:353: dgos mi 'gul gsum la gzhi bcas pas sdod pa
NK034(ngi)004:354: gsum gyi tshad zin te rtags ni lus ngag yid
NK034(ngi)004:355: la 'byung thob pa gsum gyi gzer thebs so de
NK034(ngi)004:356: las bstan du med do s+aa m+aa y+aa bstan pa
NK034(ngi)004:357: gang babs rin chen gyis legs bris mchan khung dag
NK034(ngi)004:358: tu bcang bkur sti sus byas grol bar nges 'ja'
NK034(ngi)004:359: 'od sgra dang sa g.yo dang sad ser mu ge
NK034(ngi)004:360: gzas zin dus phyogs bstun lce yis 'di bklags na
NK034(ngi)004:361: stong gsum sprul pa'i sangs rgyas la yon phul ba
NK034(ngi)004:362: bas 'di don che bstan pa thams cad kyi rang
NK034(ngi)004:363: babs rang byung byin brlabs kyi yi ge 'di rgyal
NK034(ngi)004:364: po dza ri zhes bya ba'i khab kyi lho bya
NK034(ngi)004:365: rgod spungs pa'i ri la ston pa mya ngan las
NK034(ngi)004:366: 'da' ba'i tshul bstan pa'i tshe dga' rab rdo rjes
NK034(ngi)004:367: gdung ba'i smre sngags phyung bas rin po che lnga'i
NK034(ngi)004:368: yi ge rang byung ba dga' rab rdo rje'i phyag
NK034(ngi)004:369: g.yas pa'i mthil du babs pa sangs rgyas kyi 'das
NK034(ngi)004:370: rjes tha ma bstan pa thams cad kyi bu gcig
NK034(ngi)004:371: par bkod pa'o s+aa m+aa y+aa rgya rgya rgya gser
NK034(ngi)004:372: yig canah sangs rgyas kyi 'das rjes gsum las dang
NK034(ngi)004:373: po dga' ldan nas babs pa man ngag rnams kyi
NK034(ngi)004:374: rtsa ba gnyis pa gsang chen rol pa'i dur khrod
NK034(ngi)004:375: du babs pa dang po'i 'grel ba'i tshul gsum pa
NK034(ngi)004:376: bya rgod spungs rir babs pa gnyis pa'i t+ai ka
NK034(ngi)004:377: ste 'das rjes gsum bzhugs rgya gar skad du b+hu
NK034(ngi)004:378: d+ha d+he ka ra e ka bod skad du sangs
NK034(ngi)004:379: rgyas kyi 'das rjes dang po e e e ma
NK034(ngi)004:380: rigs kyi bu lus dang ngag dang yid kyi sngon
NK034(ngi)004:381: du 'gro ba la rtsal sbyang bar bya'o rnal du
NK034(ngi)004:382: dbab pa'i cho gas sor gzhug par bya'o de ltar
NK034(ngi)004:383: byas pas sangs rgyas kyi mdzad spyod la reg pa'o
NK034(ngi)004:384: lus ni bzhugs stangs las mi 'da' bar bya'o ngag
NK034(ngi)004:385: ni smra ba'i rgyun gcod par bya'o sems ni gtad
NK034(ngi)004:386: pa'i 'ben dang mi 'bral bar bya'o des ni sangs
NK034(ngi)004:387: rgyas kyi bden pa la reg pa'o +thii kye ma
NK034(ngi)004:388: kye ma rigs kyi bu sgo dang yul dang rlung
NK034(ngi)004:389: rig gi gnad bstun par bya'o des ni chos nyid
NK034(ngi)004:390: dngos la reg pa'o rigs kyi bu de la snang
NK034(ngi)004:391: ba'i rang bzhin chos thams cad du 'gyur ro des
NK034(ngi)004:392: ni chos nyid la byan tshud pa'o zhes sum cu
NK034(ngi)004:393: rtsa gsum gyi gnas sman 'tsho byed gzhon nu'i ldum
NK034(ngi)004:394: rar rdo rje 'chang yongs su mya ngan 'das pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:395: tshul bstan pa'i tshe sprul pa po dga' rab rdo
NK034(ngi)004:396: rjes gdung ba'i smre sngags bton pa kye ma kyi
NK034(ngi)004:397: hud kye ma klong ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub
NK034(ngi)004:398: na 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel zhes brjod
NK034(ngi)004:399: pas 'od phung gi dkyil na phyag g.yas pa'i gru
NK034(ngi)004:400: mo man chod bstan nas dga' rab rdo rje'i spyi
NK034(ngi)004:401: bo dang lag mthil du rin po che shel gyi
NK034(ngi)004:402: za ma tog sen gang ba gcig babs te de
NK034(ngi)004:403: zhal phye bas rin po che mthing ga la bee
NK034(ngi)004:404: d+aur+ya mthing ga'i zhun mas bris pa babs pas dga'
NK034(ngi)004:405: rab rdo rjes rtogs pa'i gdeng rnyed do 'das rjes
NK034(ngi)004:406: dang po rdzogs so +thii rgya gar skad du b+hud+d+ha
NK034(ngi)004:407: d+he ka ra d+hu ye bod skad du sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)004:408: kyi zhal chems gnyis pa e ma ho rigs kyi
NK034(ngi)004:409: bu lus ru shan ma phyed pas khams gsum du
NK034(ngi)004:410: ldog pas na lus ru shan 'byed pa la mkhas
NK034(ngi)004:411: par bya'o ngag ru shan ma phyed na ngag khams
NK034(ngi)004:412: gsum du ldog par 'gyur bas ngag ru shan 'byed
NK034(ngi)004:413: pa la mkhas par bya'o sems ru shan ma phyed
NK034(ngi)004:414: na sems khams gsum du ldog pas na sems ru
NK034(ngi)004:415: shan 'byed pa la mkhas par bya'o de nas lus
NK034(ngi)004:416: rnal du ma phab na lus sor mi chud do
NK034(ngi)004:417: ngag rnal du ma phab na ngag sor mi chud
NK034(ngi)004:418: do de nas sems rnal du ma phab na sems
NK034(ngi)004:419: sor mi chud do e ma ho rigs kyi bu
NK034(ngi)004:420: lus yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar 'dod na
NK034(ngi)004:421: lus sku gsum gyi bzhugs stangs las mi 'da' bar
NK034(ngi)004:422: bya'o ngag yongs su mya ngan las 'da' bar 'dod
NK034(ngi)004:423: na ngag smra ba bcad pa'i 'khor lo las mi
NK034(ngi)004:424: 'da' bar bya'o rigs kyi bu sems yongs su mya
NK034(ngi)004:425: ngan las 'da' bar 'dod na yul nam mkha' stong
NK034(ngi)004:426: ba dang mi 'bral bar bya'o +thii de ni skye
NK034(ngi)004:427: ba med pa'i thabs mchog tu gsungs so snang ba
NK034(ngi)004:428: thams cad kyi chos nyid du 'char bar 'dod na
NK034(ngi)004:429: mig sku gsum gyi gzigs stangs las ma 'das par
NK034(ngi)004:430: gyis shig des ni snang ba gzigs snang thams cad
NK034(ngi)004:431: rang snang du 'char ba'i gnad do e ma hoh
NK034(ngi)004:432: rig pa la byan tshud par 'dod pa'i skyes bus
NK034(ngi)004:433: yul stong pa la rig pa stong pa gtad par
NK034(ngi)004:434: bya'o des ni yul thams cad kyi dbyings su 'da'
NK034(ngi)004:435: bar 'gyur ro e ma hoh 'gyu ba rang sar
NK034(ngi)004:436: grol bar 'dod na rlung rab tu dal ba brten
NK034(ngi)004:437: par bya'o e ma hoh des ni khams gsum 'khor
NK034(ngi)004:438: lo rgyun bcad par 'gyur ba'i man ngag go e
NK034(ngi)004:439: ma hoh de ltar snang ba bzhi'i chos nyid skyes
NK034(ngi)004:440: pa las 'khrul pa'i snang ba rgyun chad pa'o e
NK034(ngi)004:441: ma hoh rigs kyi bu mi 'gul ba gsum la
NK034(ngi)004:442: gzhi chos +thii sdod pa gsum gyis tshad zungs shig
NK034(ngi)004:443: so phag shi tham thob pa gsum gyis gzer thob
NK034(ngi)004:444: cig sa ma y+aa de ltar sus byed pa khams
NK034(ngi)004:445: gsum du ldog re kan dbu rgya 'gar ba lam
NK034(ngi)004:446: zhes dur khrod chen po me ri 'bar bar sprul
NK034(ngi)004:447: sku mya ngan las 'das pa'i tshul bstan pa'i tshe
NK034(ngi)004:448: dga' rab rdo rje brgyal zhing sa la 'gyel nas
NK034(ngi)004:449: gdung ba'i smre sngags bton pa kye ma kyi hud
NK034(ngi)004:450: kye ma klong ston pa sgron me'i 'od nub na
NK034(ngi)004:451: 'jig rten mun pa gang gis sel zhes pa brgyal
NK034(ngi)004:452: sangs nas brjod pas nam mkha' 'od phung gi dkyil
NK034(ngi)004:453: nas phyag g.yas pa'i gru mo man chad bstan nas
NK034(ngi)004:454: rin po che rab tu 'od 'bar ba khyad par
NK034(ngi)004:455: gyi yi ge babs pa tsam gyis yun gyi sgrib
NK034(ngi)004:456: pa ma sbyangs gnas su dag go mkha' 'gro ma'i
NK034(ngi)004:457: gnas su snang bar byas so sangs rgyas kyi 'das
NK034(ngi)004:458: rjes gnyis pa rdzogs so +thii rgya gar skad du
NK034(ngi)004:459: b+hud+d+ha d+he ka ra tri bod skad du sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)004:460: kyi zhal chems gsum pa zag pa rang zad snang
NK034(ngi)004:461: ba rang sar grol ba la phyag 'tshal lo kye
NK034(ngi)004:462: ma kye ma rigs kyi bu sngon du 'gro ba'i
NK034(ngi)004:463: gnad la mkhas na mchog dang thun mong gi dgos
NK034(ngi)004:464: pa la mkhas par 'gyur ro de yang lus kyis
NK034(ngi)004:465: bya byed 'khor lo bskor ngag ni ca co'i 'khor
NK034(ngi)004:466: lo bskor sems ni 'phro 'du'i 'khor lo bskor de
NK034(ngi)004:467: ltar bya byed 'khor lo las 'das pa med pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:468: chos nyid la 'khor lo zhes kyi ming nas med
NK034(ngi)004:469: bar chod sel dang zhen pa log sdig pa ma
NK034(ngi)004:470: lus 'dag par ni thun mong gyur pa'i dgos pa'o
NK034(ngi)004:471: mchog la khams gsum mi 'jug dang so so'i sku
NK034(ngi)004:472: ru grol ba dang sku gsung thugs su 'das pa
NK034(ngi)004:473: yis 'di dus spyod par byas pa'o de yis lus
NK034(ngi)004:474: kyi 'brel chad nas khams gsum dag tu ldog pa
NK034(ngi)004:475: min lus dang ngag dang sems nyid la rnal du
NK034(ngi)004:476: phebs la mkhas par bya des ni lus ngag sor
NK034(ngi)004:477: chud nas nyams len nyid la brtson par 'gyur de
NK034(ngi)004:478: ltar sngon 'gro rdzogs byas nas de dag blo yis
NK034(ngi)004:479: bor byas la da ni mngon sum tig la dbab
NK034(ngi)004:480: ces pa'o e ma hoh rigs kyi bu lus kyi
NK034(ngi)004:481: gnad du chos kyi sku'i bzhugs stangs seng ge lta
NK034(ngi)004:482: bu dang sprul pa sku'i bzhugs stangs ni drang srong
NK034(ngi)004:483: tsog pu'i rnam pa lta bu'o de nyid las ma
NK034(ngi)004:484: 'das na sangs rgyas thams cad kyi sku'i klong du
NK034(ngi)004:485: mya ngan las 'da' bar 'gyur ro ngag ni bslab
NK034(ngi)004:486: par bya ba'i rim pa dang gnas dang brtan zhing
NK034(ngi)004:487: la bzla ba las mi 'da' bar bya'o de ltar
NK034(ngi)004:488: byas pas sangs rgyas kyi gsung gi klong du mya
NK034(ngi)004:489: ngan las 'da' bar gyur ro +thii sgo ni bzlog
NK034(ngi)004:490: phab zur gyis ni gzigs stangs rnam pa gsum du
NK034(ngi)004:491: grags chos sku longs sku sprul sku yi gzigs stangs
NK034(ngi)004:492: gsum las mi 'ada'o yul ni sprin bral nam mkha'
NK034(ngi)004:493: la rig pa stong pa 'char ba'o rlung ni dal
NK034(ngi)004:494: ba brten pa yis 'gro drug 'khrul pa'i rgyun chad
NK034(ngi)004:495: do mngon sum gnad 'di sus mthong ba khams gsum
NK034(ngi)004:496: ldog pa ma yin no +thii chos nyid mngon sum
NK034(ngi)004:497: snang ba yis yid dpyod 'dzin pa'i lta ba nub
NK034(ngi)004:498: nyams snang gong du 'phel ba yis bar do'i ye
NK034(ngi)004:499: shes mngon du byas rig pa tshad phebs snang ba
NK034(ngi)004:500: yis longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ngos zin chos nyid
NK034(ngi)004:501: zad pa'i snang ba yis rdzogs chen bya bral 'bras
NK034(ngi)004:502: bu thob 'di ltar bzhi la mthar phyin na myang
NK034(ngi)004:503: 'das gzhan du btsal mi dgos +thii mig dang lus
NK034(ngi)004:504: dang rig pa nyid 'gul ba med par gnad zin
NK034(ngi)004:505: na mngon sum gnad la phebs pa'o lus dang snang
NK034(ngi)004:506: ba rlung nyid kyang byas pa med par sdod pa'o
NK034(ngi)004:507: chos nyid dal bas grub pa'o skye dang 'jug dang
NK034(ngi)004:508: rlung sems la su yis rang dbang thob pa'i mi
NK034(ngi)004:509: sangs rgyas dgongs pa'i drod rnyed do +thii bstan pa
NK034(ngi)004:510: gang la dbang ba yi kha dog gis ni legs
NK034(ngi)004:511: bris nas mchan khung g.yas su bzung byas te rtag
NK034(ngi)004:512: tu bkur sti sus byas pa 'bad pa med par
NK034(ngi)004:513: grol bar nges nyi zla gza' yis zin pa dang
NK034(ngi)004:514: sgra dang sa g.yos mu ge'i dus rdo rje'i lce
NK034(ngi)004:515: yis 'di bklags na stong gsum sprul pa'i sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)004:516: la yon phul bas ni 'di don che bstan pa
NK034(ngi)004:517: thams cad kyi rtsa ba rang byung gi yi ge
NK034(ngi)004:518: las bkod pa byin brlabs kyi brgyud pa'i gnad su
NK034(ngi)004:519: la babs pa 'bad pa med par grol ba la
NK034(ngi)004:520: the tshom med do lho phyogs bde ldan yid 'dres
NK034(ngi)004:521: pa bya rgod spungs pa'i ri la ston pa mya
NK034(ngi)004:522: ngan las 'das tshul bstan pa'i tshe sprul pa po
NK034(ngi)004:523: dga' rab rdo rje'i phyag g.yas pa'i mthil du babs
NK034(ngi)004:524: pa sangs rgyas kyi 'das rjes gsum zhal chems su
NK034(ngi)004:525: bkod pa rang byung ba bstan pa thams cad kyi
NK034(ngi)004:526: bu gcig po rdzogs so 'di nyid bcangs pa tsam
NK034(ngi)004:527: gyis ni sangs rgyas rnams kyi dgongs pa thob rang
NK034(ngi)004:528: rig byin rlabs rgyud brten nas ngan song 'khor ba
NK034(ngi)004:529: dong sprug go 'di ni bshad cing bstan pa min
NK034(ngi)004:530: rab tu gsang la lus la brten dngos grub kun
NK034(ngi)004:531: gyi rtsa bar 'byung g+hu h+ya sa ma ya so
NK034(ngi)004:532: phag shi tham rin po che brgya rtsa ni rgyu
NK034(ngi)004:533: las rang byung ba'o 'dzam bu'i gling gzhan med par
NK034(ngi)004:534: yid ches so +thii gser yig can rig 'dzin gyi
NK034(ngi)004:535: 'das rjes bzhi zhar 'byung dang bcas pa bzhugs so
NK034(ngi)004:536: dga' rab rdo rje'i tshig gsum gnad du brdeg pa
NK034(ngi)004:537: bzhugs na mo sh+r+ai gu ru ye rang rig rtogs
NK034(ngi)004:538: pa'i gdeng la phyag 'tshal lo yin gzhi yi ngo
NK034(ngi)004:539: bo gnas tshul pa grub pa med pa'i rig pa
NK034(ngi)004:540: 'di rang snang 'char tshul cir yang sna tshogs su
NK034(ngi)004:541: snang ba ma 'gags pas snang zhing srid pa'i chos
NK034(ngi)004:542: kun kyang chos sku'i zhing du shar shar ba de
NK034(ngi)004:543: nyid rang gi rig pa nyid kyi thog tu grol
NK034(ngi)004:544: de don bde gshegs kun gyi thugs gnyis su med
NK034(ngi)004:545: pa'i ye shes kyi dgongs pa thams cad 'dir 'dus
NK034(ngi)004:546: pa brgyal 'jam dpal bshes gnyen ba bslang phyir tshig
NK034(ngi)004:547: gsum gnad du brdeg pa'i man ngag 'di 'khor 'das
NK034(ngi)004:548: gnyis kyi rdos thag bcad gnyis ka rang yin par
NK034(ngi)004:549: shes pas pa'i phyir 'chi ma kha'i zhal chems shin
NK034(ngi)004:550: tu dam par bzung bar bstan pa ni snying gi
NK034(ngi)004:551: dkyil du sbos a skye med du la bzla ba'o
NK034(ngi)004:552: ita&&& rig pa spyi brtol du bstan pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)004:553: ni ngo rang thog tu sprad pa rig pa nyid
NK034(ngi)004:554: rig pa nyid du rang ngo rnam dag tu bstan
NK034(ngi)004:555: pa zhe sdang nyid zhe sdang nyid kyis grol bar
NK034(ngi)004:556: ngo sprad pa'o dang thag gcig thog tu bcad pa
NK034(ngi)004:557: gnyis med shes pa'i rig pa dang gdeng grol thog
NK034(ngi)004:558: tu bca' de'i phyir rang rig rang gis grol ba'o
NK034(ngi)004:559: ba'o rang ngo yin pa thams cad rang snang du
NK034(ngi)004:560: ma grol ba gcig kyang med gzhan ngo snang tshul
NK034(ngi)004:561: ma rtogs pa la rang gzhan gnyis su byung gnyis
NK034(ngi)004:562: 'dres pa rang thog tu rang grol ba'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)004:563: gcig ngo gcig la bkal ba mi mdzes te gcig
NK034(ngi)004:564: gis chog pa'o 'phrad pa'o ita&&& cir snang rang yin
NK034(ngi)004:565: ma yin pa'i chos logs nas mi rnyed stobs rang
NK034(ngi)004:566: gi des na rigs mthun gyis rigs mthun grol te
NK034(ngi)004:567: gnyen po gzhan med pa'o rang che rang rang phrad
NK034(ngi)004:568: pa'o ni dper na skad rigs mthun pa'i mi skad
NK034(ngi)004:569: mi mthun pa'i yul gang du phrad kyang rang du
NK034(ngi)004:570: shes pa ltar zhe sdang du shes pas grol ma
NK034(ngi)004:571: thog tu ma rang phrad snang ba nyid snang bas
NK034(ngi)004:572: grol te dper na mar la mar thim pa lta
NK034(ngi)004:573: bu'o bu thog tu rang phrad rig pa nyid rig
NK034(ngi)004:574: pas grol te chu la chu thim pa lta bu'o
NK034(ngi)004:575: gcig thog tu gcig rang rang ngo rang du phrad
NK034(ngi)004:576: pa ngo bo brjod las 'das pa dper na nam
NK034(ngi)004:577: mkha' la nam mkha' thim pa'am sbrul gyi mdud gsum
NK034(ngi)004:578: dus gcig la grol ba lta bu'o phrad pa'o rig
NK034(ngi)004:579: pa gcig pu rang dang 'brel ba de ltar na
NK034(ngi)004:580: rang gi ngo bo shes na dus gcig la thams
NK034(ngi)004:581: cad 'dus shing ngo bo gcig las ma 'das pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:582: ye shes dper na yid mthun pa'i pho mo dben
NK034(ngi)004:583: par phrad pa lta bu'o rang gcig pu sna tshogs
NK034(ngi)004:584: su snang yang tha dad nyid tha dad nyid kyis
NK034(ngi)004:585: grol ba'i ye shes spyi mdud gcig bcad pas do
NK034(ngi)004:586: thag brgya chad pa lta bu'o rang dang 'brel ba
NK034(ngi)004:587: grol ba gcig pu rang dang 'brel ba ni rang
NK034(ngi)004:588: snang yin pas gzhan du mi rnyed pa'i ye shes
NK034(ngi)004:589: te ye shes nyid du'o dper na lam brgya stong
NK034(ngi)004:590: gi mtha' grong khyer gcig la zug pa lta bu'o
NK034(ngi)004:591: 'o rang thog tu mthar snang gi thag chod de
NK034(ngi)004:592: ltar rang gis rang ngo shes pas ma rig pa
NK034(ngi)004:593: dang gnyis su med pa ste dper na mi gcig
NK034(ngi)004:594: la ming mang po yod pa gang nas bos kyang
NK034(ngi)004:595: 'ong ba don gcig las ma 'das pa lta bu'o
NK034(ngi)004:596: gcig thog tu rang snang gi thag chod grol thog
NK034(ngi)004:597: tu the tshom gyi thag chod pa'o rang gis rang
NK034(ngi)004:598: grol te rig pa grol ba ste de ltar rang
NK034(ngi)004:599: yin par ngo shes pas rtogs pa thams cad rang
NK034(ngi)004:600: sar grol bas sngar 'dris kyi mi phyis mthong ba
NK034(ngi)004:601: lta bu'o +thii rang la byan tshud pa phyug 'gyu
NK034(ngi)004:602: ba thams cad rang sar grol ba dper na bang
NK034(ngi)004:603: mdzod la ci 'dod pa lta bu'o po'i bang mdzod
NK034(ngi)004:604: lta bu'i gdeng gzhan la byan tshud pa rig pa
NK034(ngi)004:605: mngon sum du snang ba la gzhan ma grub pas
NK034(ngi)004:606: gling bzhi la dbang bsgyur ba lta bu /
NK034(ngi)004:607: de yang 'byung ba la dbang bsgyur nus pa ste
NK034(ngi)004:608: rkyen rkyen gyis grol bas dbang po gzhan la rag
NK034(ngi)004:609: ma lus pa'o 'khor los sgyur ba'i rgyal po lta
NK034(ngi)004:610: bu'i gdeng grol sa la chos nyid ka dag dri
NK034(ngi)004:611: ma med pa la rang sar grol ba nam mkha'
NK034(ngi)004:612: la nam mkha' thim pa'am mkha' la sprin dengs pa
NK034(ngi)004:613: lta bu'o byan tshud pa mkha' la mkha' thim pa
NK034(ngi)004:614: lta bu'i gdeng ngo +thii rang thog tu rang grol
NK034(ngi)004:615: rang rang gis grol ba rdo bas rdo bcag pa
NK034(ngi)004:616: lta bu dang lcags kyis lcags 'joms pa ltar dri
NK034(ngi)004:617: mas dri ma dag pa'o gcig thog tu gcig grol
NK034(ngi)004:618: ba ni me las me len pa chu la chu
NK034(ngi)004:619: 'pho ba lta bu mar la mar bsnan pa lta
NK034(ngi)004:620: bu'o ma bu gnyis sbyor ba'o rang gi ma rang
NK034(ngi)004:621: yin pas stong pas stong pa grol bas rig pa
NK034(ngi)004:622: snang ba la thim pa'o +thii rang ngo zhes pas
NK034(ngi)004:623: gzhi dang ngo phrad pa'o rang gi rang snang du
NK034(ngi)004:624: shes pa dpe me long nang du bzhin mthong ba
NK034(ngi)004:625: lta bu'o de'i phyir na yid ches pas ma dang
NK034(ngi)004:626: bu phrad pa lta bu ste grol sa gcig pu
NK034(ngi)004:627: yin par ngo shes rang gi rang thog tu grol
NK034(ngi)004:628: bas snang ba stong pa la gsal ba rig par
NK034(ngi)004:629: ngo shes pa'o pa'o rang gi rang grol bar shes
NK034(ngi)004:630: pas thog ma 'khor ba rang gis shes pa de
NK034(ngi)004:631: 'das pa la 'das par shes pa ma rig pa
NK034(ngi)004:632: rang grol ba yin no rig pa nyid la thag
NK034(ngi)004:633: bcad pa'o de phyir dpe dngos dri mas dri ma
NK034(ngi)004:634: 'khru ba dang rnam don rang yin pa'i phyir rtog
NK034(ngi)004:635: nyid la rnam rtog ste gnyen po gzhan la rag
NK034(ngi)004:636: ma lus par thag bcad do gzhi nyid las chu
NK034(ngi)004:637: la chu bzhag dang mar la mar bzhag pa lta
NK034(ngi)004:638: bu grol bas gdeng gang yin tu bca' ba'o de'i
NK034(ngi)004:639: phyir sbrul gyi mdud pa nyid sbrul rang gis grol
NK034(ngi)004:640: ba lta bu ste gzhan ltos kyi rig pa rang
NK034(ngi)004:641: gi thog tu grol bas rig pa rang gnas tshi
NK034(ngi)004:642: chad pas dngos gzhi rang thog tu gzhi bca' ba'o
NK034(ngi)004:643: +thii dga' rab rdo rje yongs su mya ngan las
NK034(ngi)004:644: 'da' ba'i tshul bstan pa'i tshe 'jam dpal bshes gnyen
NK034(ngi)004:645: brgyal zhing sa la 'gyel nas kye ma kyi hud
NK034(ngi)004:646: ces sgra chen po phyungs pas ro langs bde ba
NK034(ngi)004:647: 'od kyi dkyil nas phyag g.yas pa phyungs te brgyal
NK034(ngi)004:648: 'jal dpal bshes gnyen ba slong ba'i don du gsang
NK034(ngi)004:649: ba'i zhal chems tshig gang zag gcig grol ba'i gsum
NK034(ngi)004:650: gnad du brdeg pa phyag g.yas pa'i mthil du bee
NK034(ngi)004:651: d+aur+ya mthing kha zhun mas rang nan tu bris pa
NK034(ngi)004:652: babs te rin po che shel gyi za ma tog
NK034(ngi)004:653: sen gang ba cig snod du babs pas 'jam dpal
NK034(ngi)004:654: bshes gnyen brgyal ba las grol bar gyur cing rtogs
NK034(ngi)004:655: pa'i gdeng dang ldan par 'gyur to de'i phyir na
NK034(ngi)004:656: gzhan la gsang ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du sba
NK034(ngi)004:657: bar bya'o 'chi kha ma'i zhal gdams tshig gsum rgyud
NK034(ngi)004:658: thams cad kyi bcud phyungs pa lta ba'i don gser
NK034(ngi)004:659: lta bur bstan pa dur khrod chen po bsil ba
NK034(ngi)004:660: tshal du babs pa chu bo dan tig mgor snang
NK034(ngi)004:661: bar byas pa'i gdams ngag dam pa sems can thams
NK034(ngi)004:662: cad dbugs 'byin par byed pa'i lam sangs rgyas kyi
NK034(ngi)004:663: zhing skad cig la grol bar byed pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)004:664: rdzogs 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi sgom nyams drug pa
NK034(ngi)004:665: bzhugs so na mo sh+r+ai gu ru ye rang rig
NK034(ngi)004:666: rtogs pa'i gdeng la phyag 'tshal lo gzhi yi gnas
NK034(ngi)004:667: lugs yin pa grub pa med pa'i rig pa 'di
NK034(ngi)004:668: rang snang snang ba sna tshogs su 'char tshul cir
NK034(ngi)004:669: yang ma nges pas snang srid kun kyang thams cad
NK034(ngi)004:670: rang snang yin par shes pas chos sku'i zhing du
NK034(ngi)004:671: 'char shar ba de nyid rang rang snang nyid du
NK034(ngi)004:672: grol gi thog der grol de don bde gshegs kun
NK034(ngi)004:673: gyi dgongs pa ni sangs rgyas kyi thugs gnyis su
NK034(ngi)004:674: med pa'i ye shes brgyal 'jam dpal gnyen gyi sa
NK034(ngi)004:675: sh+r+ai sing ha ba bslang phyir tshig drug man ngag
NK034(ngi)004:676: ni 'khor 'das gnyis ka rang snang yin par shes
NK034(ngi)004:677: pa'i man ngag kyi srog thag bcad pa'i phyir 'chi
NK034(ngi)004:678: kha'i zhal chems rang sems rnam dag tu bstan pa
NK034(ngi)004:679: rig pa spyi btol du bstan pa'i gdams ngag ni
NK034(ngi)004:680: snying gi dkyil du sbos shin tu dam par s+aa
NK034(ngi)004:681: m+aa y+aa dam tshig dgongs pa mnyam par zhog cig
NK034(ngi)004:682: ma ti tra ma dgongs pa rang la gnas pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:683: gding la phyag 'tshal lo don gyi dgongs pa sgom
NK034(ngi)004:684: pa'i nyams drug tu bstan pa ye shes chen po'i
NK034(ngi)004:685: lung 'di ni yul la nam mkha' stong pa snang
NK034(ngi)004:686: ba'i ye shes chen po de ri dper na dwags
NK034(ngi)004:687: rgyal ji ltar tshud pa bzhin bya byed bral ba'i
NK034(ngi)004:688: mkha' la nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba la mig
NK034(ngi)004:689: dang rig pa gtad de brtag par bya'o ji ltar
NK034(ngi)004:690: 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bdag gi blo la dgongs shar
NK034(ngi)004:691: ba'i brgyal ba bslang phyir don gyi dgongs pa'i zhal
NK034(ngi)004:692: chems 'di rig pa'i gtad sa lus kyi 'dug stangs
NK034(ngi)004:693: dag mig gi gnad dang bstun dgongs pa'i don man
NK034(ngi)004:694: ngag gi gnad drug drug gis phyi nas bstan kye
NK034(ngi)004:695: ma kye ma rigs kyi bu sh+r+ai sing ha la
NK034(ngi)004:696: bos nas chen po don gyi rig pa dri ma
NK034(ngi)004:697: dang bral ba gcer bu mngon sum lu gu rgyud
NK034(ngi)004:698: du lta bar 'dod na rig pa'i yul btsal nam
NK034(ngi)004:699: mkha' sprin bral ba dang lus kyi 'dug stangs gnad
NK034(ngi)004:700: gzir ba dang 'gro 'ong gi lam rlung phyir 'dzin
NK034(ngi)004:701: bcad pa dang gtad sa'i 'ben dbyings gnad gzung ba
NK034(ngi)004:702: dang mi 'gul ba gsum la gzhi bca' ba dang
NK034(ngi)004:703: rgya che ba'i nam mkha' la spar gyis rig pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:704: rang ngo zin pa bzung pa'o thog ma ka dag
NK034(ngi)004:705: babs kyi 'khrul ma myong ba'i spyi gzhi /
NK034(ngi)004:706: yul dang 'khrul pa snang ba lhun grub kyi ma
NK034(ngi)004:707: rig pa'i bag chags rgyud la langs pa'o yul dang
NK034(ngi)004:708: gnas pa brten pa lus kyi yul rang gi snying
NK034(ngi)004:709: gi dkyil na rig pa'i rten gnas so dang nyams
NK034(ngi)004:710: su blang bya nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba'i yul
NK034(ngi)004:711: dang nam mkha' la rig pa mngon sum du snang
NK034(ngi)004:712: ji ltar snang na lu gu rgyud du snang ba'o
NK034(ngi)004:713: gsal ba dngos snang kha dog 'od kyi yul de
NK034(ngi)004:714: yang 'od dang thig le dang sku'i snang ba dus
NK034(ngi)004:715: 'di nyid la 'char ro dang tha ma 'gro sa
NK034(ngi)004:716: rang snang bar do'i yul rang gi rig pa ye
NK034(ngi)004:717: shes 'od sku'i rnam par snang zhing bems por ma
NK034(ngi)004:718: grub da lta de'i don nyams su blangs pas 'od
NK034(ngi)004:719: snang 'di nyid la gtan la phebs pas bar chod
NK034(ngi)004:720: med par sangs rgya'o lo seng ge'i 'dug stangs rkang
NK034(ngi)004:721: mthil gnyis sprad pus mo phyir bsgrad mjing pa yid
NK034(ngi)004:722: tsam gyen la bteg ste stod seng ge ltar bya
NK034(ngi)004:723: ste mig nam mkha' la gtad kyis rig pa gcun
NK034(ngi)004:724: pa dang glang po che'i 'dug stangs kyis lta ba
NK034(ngi)004:725: mig mi 'dzum par nam mkha' la har por lta
NK034(ngi)004:726: g.yas g.yon du mi lta'o dang 'dab chags kyi lding
NK034(ngi)004:727: thabs kyis lta ba mig de yang nam mkha' nyid
NK034(ngi)004:728: dang ma bral bar yid tsam gyen la lta'o spyi
NK034(ngi)004:729: rgya rlabs kyis gcod pa dang wa mo'i zur 'gros
NK034(ngi)004:730: kyis sa mnan pa dang de yang nam mkha' sprin
NK034(ngi)004:731: dang bral ba'i dus su ri rtse la song la
NK034(ngi)004:732: mig g.yas kyi zur gyis mnan te dpung pa'i steng
NK034(ngi)004:733: du lkog ma bzhag la lta skyes bu'i rgyang thabs
NK034(ngi)004:734: kyis de yang dben par gan rkyal du nyal te
NK034(ngi)004:735: yan lag bzhi ka thar rtse brgyangs la mig steng
NK034(ngi)004:736: du lta'o bar snang du yid bzung ba dang rgya
NK034(ngi)004:737: mdud kyi dril lugs kyis rang gi shes pa mig
NK034(ngi)004:738: tu dril te thig le dang 'du 'bral med par
NK034(ngi)004:739: brtag go lu gu rgyud kyi khungs bcad pa'o kha
NK034(ngi)004:740: sna'i dbugs yud tsam nang du 'then dbugs khad kyis
NK034(ngi)004:741: bsdams la yang rim gyis phar la btang ste 'og
NK034(ngi)004:743: pas ma rig pa las kyi rlung ldog shes pa
NK034(ngi)004:744: ni mig nam mkha' la ma 'gul bar gtad pas
NK034(ngi)004:745: rnam rtog gi rgyu 'grul chod rig pa mig tu
NK034(ngi)004:746: bcug pas zla ba phyed ma 'gags bar lta'o ngo
NK034(ngi)004:747: bo la 'khrul pa med dbyings phyi nang 'dres pas
NK034(ngi)004:748: nam mkha' dang dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgron ma
NK034(ngi)004:749: dbyings kyi go rar chud pas rig pa la 'gro
NK034(ngi)004:750: sa med de nyid dbyings dang ma bral bas yid
NK034(ngi)004:751: kyi rnam rtog chod rig pa dbyings dang phyi nang
NK034(ngi)004:752: gnyis 'dres pas 'khrul pa gzhi la sangs pa'o nam
NK034(ngi)004:753: mkha' sprin dang bral ba dang dbyings rnam par dag
NK034(ngi)004:754: pa dri ma dang bral ba dang snang ba sgrib
NK034(ngi)004:755: g.yogs dang bral ba dang thig le spro bsdu dang
NK034(ngi)004:756: bral ba dang mig zur mnan te yid tsam gyen
NK034(ngi)004:757: la bzlog pas 'ja' tshon gyi rnam pa lta bu
NK034(ngi)004:758: la gug ge ba mthing shas che ba 'char bas
NK034(ngi)004:759: de la mig gtad ste de ltar 'od zer la
NK034(ngi)004:760: gtad pas snang ba thams cad rim gyis 'od du
NK034(ngi)004:761: 'char ro de nyid rig pa yin no shar kyang
NK034(ngi)004:762: 'od de nyung 'bru tsam 'gro zhing de la gtad
NK034(ngi)004:763: na rim gyis rgya che ba'i thig le 'char ro
NK034(ngi)004:764: de la goms pas snang srid thams cad 'od dang
NK034(ngi)004:765: thig le skur 'gyur ro 'od snang gsal 'grib bral
NK034(ngi)004:766: ba dang de ltar goms pas snang srid thams cad
NK034(ngi)004:767: 'od dang thig ler 'char bas bar do la rag
NK034(ngi)004:768: ma lus pa 'tshang rgya'o lu gu rgyud 'gro 'ong
NK034(ngi)004:769: dang bral de ltar 'od kyi dbyings de nyid kyi
NK034(ngi)004:770: nang du rang gi rig pa'i ngo bo de lu
NK034(ngi)004:771: gu rgyud lcags sgrog lta bu'i 'od zer lnga tshang
NK034(ngi)004:772: ba thig le nyung 'bru tsam lnga'i cha tshang bar
NK034(ngi)004:773: 'char te de yang bzung bar dka' bas de la
NK034(ngi)004:774: mig gtad pas thams cad sku'i snang bar 'char ro
NK034(ngi)004:775: de ni rig pa'i ngo bo zin pa'o la rang
NK034(ngi)004:776: gi de bzhin nyid gtad pa'o lus mi 'gul 'dug
NK034(ngi)004:777: stangs gong du bstan pa las ma zhig par gnas
NK034(ngi)004:778: pa'o bas snang ba bzhi la bzhag pa dang mig
NK034(ngi)004:779: ma 'gul bas g.yas g.yon du mi 'gul bar lu
NK034(ngi)004:780: gu rgyud la gtad de bya byed dang bral bar
NK034(ngi)004:781: lta'o lu gu rgyud la gzer thebs pa dang rig
NK034(ngi)004:782: pa ma 'gul bas de ltar mig de nyid la
NK034(ngi)004:783: gtad pas lu gu rgyud mi 'gul bas rtog med
NK034(ngi)004:784: chos sku zang thal lo snang srid chos skur grol
NK034(ngi)004:785: ba dang de nyid ma 'gul bas lta ba'i rang
NK034(ngi)004:786: sa zin pas 'khrul pa ka nas dag pa'o 'khrul
NK034(ngi)004:787: pa'i snang ba rgyun chad pa dang de ltar chos
NK034(ngi)004:788: sku 'gul ba med pas de nyid chos sku yin
NK034(ngi)004:789: pas gzhan nas tshol ba tshi chad pa las gnyen
NK034(ngi)004:790: po mi 'gyur bas de dang ma bral bar gnas
NK034(ngi)004:791: par bya'o ye shes ngos zin pa dang stong pa
NK034(ngi)004:792: las 'gul ba med pas sku dang thig le'i snang
NK034(ngi)004:793: ba de yang brtags na dngos po gang du'ang ma
NK034(ngi)004:794: grub par 'dug pas chos sku yin pas dngos por
NK034(ngi)004:795: grub pa med ces bya ste yid kyi rtog pa
NK034(ngi)004:796: thams cad zad pas stong pa gsal bar nyams su
NK034(ngi)004:797: myong ba'o 'gyu byed rang sar dwangs pa'o snang srid
NK034(ngi)004:798: rig stong gsal bar shar bas 'od dang 'od khyim
NK034(ngi)004:799: dang rig pa dang rig pa'i sku dang thig le
NK034(ngi)004:800: dang phyed sku la sogs shar bas thams cad rig
NK034(ngi)004:801: pa'i ngo bo lu gu rgyud sna tshogs su shar
NK034(ngi)004:802: brtan pa'i tshad ni rtsal las shes par bya'o bems
NK034(ngi)004:803: po las grol ba dang nam mkha'i khams su lu
NK034(ngi)004:804: gu rgyud kyis khyab pas chos nyid ma thog tu
NK034(ngi)004:805: grol ba dang cir snang 'od snang las ma 'das
NK034(ngi)004:806: pas 'byung ba lnga'i bdud las grol ba ye shes
NK034(ngi)004:807: lnga'i cha las 'od lnga rig pa'i yul du shar
NK034(ngi)004:808: bas ngam grog dang g.yang sa 'gags te snang srid
NK034(ngi)004:809: gzhal yas khang du shar bas lha'i dkyil 'khor sgom
NK034(ngi)004:810: mi dgos dang 'khor 'das rang ngo shes pas rig
NK034(ngi)004:811: pa'i ngo bo lu gu rgyud cer mthong du mthong
NK034(ngi)004:812: bas rkyen gzhan la rag ma lus te rang yin
NK034(ngi)004:813: pas gzhan la ltos mi dgos pa'i gnad ka'o ltos
NK034(ngi)004:814: pa'i chos las grol ba dang stong pa gsal ba
NK034(ngi)004:815: rig par 'dres pas rig pa nyid bems po ma
NK034(ngi)004:816: yin pas rig pa dngos po las 'das pa stong
NK034(ngi)004:817: pa nyams su myong ba'i gsal cha'o rgyud lung gi
NK034(ngi)004:818: tshig las grol ba dang dag pa'i dbyings rgya bskyed
NK034(ngi)004:819: pas rig pa rang thog tu spar gyis zin pa
NK034(ngi)004:820: ces bya'o de ltar gzhan snang ma yin rang snang
NK034(ngi)004:821: yin gzhan nas byung ba ma yiin rang byung ni
NK034(ngi)004:822: gzhan shar ba ma yin rang shar yin gzhan gyis
NK034(ngi)004:823: byas pa ma yin rang yod yin no +thii 'jam
NK034(ngi)004:824: dpal bshes gnyen dgongs pa yongs su mya ngan las
NK034(ngi)004:825: 'da' ba'i tshe 'od zer gyi phung po dang bcas
NK034(ngi)004:826: te nam mkha' la gshegs pas sh+r+ai sing ha brgyal
NK034(ngi)004:827: zhing sa la 'gyel bar gyur te kyi hud kyi
NK034(ngi)004:828: sgra chen po phyogs bcur 'bod cing gnas pa las
NK034(ngi)004:829: nam mkhar sgra chen po zhig grags par gyur te
NK034(ngi)004:830: de nyid brgyal ba sangs nas bltas pas nam mkha'
NK034(ngi)004:831: 'od phung gi dkyil nas many+dzu sh+r+ais phyag g.yas pa
NK034(ngi)004:832: phyungs te brgyal ba bslang ba'i don du sh+r+ai sing
NK034(ngi)004:833: ha'i phyag mthil du rin po che za ma tog
NK034(ngi)004:834: gi nang du bee d+aur+ya mthing kha zhun mas rang
NK034(ngi)004:835: nan du bris pa gcig dur khrod chen po so
NK034(ngi)004:836: sa gling de nyid du babs so de nyid babs
NK034(ngi)004:837: pa tsam gyis rtogs pa'i gdeng dang ldan par gyur
NK034(ngi)004:838: to 'di ni 'jal dpal bshes gnyen gyi zhal chems
NK034(ngi)004:839: sgom nyams drug gis skye med stong pa'i klong du
NK034(ngi)004:840: mya ngan las 'da' bar byed pa'i man ngag gsang
NK034(ngi)004:841: ba bas kyang ches gsang bar gyur pa nyams su
NK034(ngi)004:842: blang ba'i phyogs su bstan pa rdzogs so sh+r+ai sing
NK034(ngi)004:843: ha'i gzer bu bdun pa bzhugs so sarba san+ti ka
NK034(ngi)004:844: stong gsal shes rab rdzogs la phyag 'tshal lo kun
NK034(ngi)004:845: tu khyab cing sna tshogs snang ba rang gi rig
NK034(ngi)004:846: pa'i ye shes de thams cad la shar zhing snang
NK034(ngi)004:847: ba ste rig pa yul thams cad la 'jug cing
NK034(ngi)004:848: khyab pa de la gal mdo'i gcan phrang du gzer
NK034(ngi)004:849: gdab pa ni yi rig pa'i ye shes rgya yan
NK034(ngi)004:850: phyogs med sh+r+ai sing ha'i ltar rang gi rig pa
NK034(ngi)004:851: nyid 'gyur ba med pa ngo bo ka nas dag
NK034(ngi)004:852: pa'i ye shes ye nas yin par shes pas shes
NK034(ngi)004:853: bya'i dri mas ma gos par snang ba'o de mi
NK034(ngi)004:854: 'gyur sa la gzer chen btab pa'i phyir chos thams
NK034(ngi)004:855: cad mi 'gyur ba'i ti ka rdo rje'i phreng ba
NK034(ngi)004:856: zhes so 'khor 'das gnyis po bsre 'phrang la gzer
NK034(ngi)004:857: chen bdun pa'i man ngag dgongs pa bdun gyi drod
NK034(ngi)004:858: tshad bdun gyis tha ma snod bcud rang grol du
NK034(ngi)004:859: shes pa'o bdun ni 'khor 'das gnyis kyi 'phrang dang
NK034(ngi)004:860: blo dngos gnyis rtag chad gnyis yul sems gnyis chos
NK034(ngi)004:861: can chos nyid gnyis byings rgod gnyis snang stong gnyis
NK034(ngi)004:862: su med par bsre ba dang bdun no btab pas
NK034(ngi)004:863: mi 'gyur bde chen bdag gi blo la mi 'dod
NK034(ngi)004:864: kyang 'di rang mi legs phyi nang gi rtags sna
NK034(ngi)004:865: tshogs shar de don man ngag nyi ma'i zer 'dra
NK034(ngi)004:866: ba brgyal ba bud+d+ha'i dgongs pa ni thugs las 'das
NK034(ngi)004:867: pa ma rig pa'i mig 'byed pa 'di ye shes
NK034(ngi)004:868: mdo brgyal ba bslang phyir rgyud kun gyi bcud phyungs
NK034(ngi)004:869: ba las bslang phyir dgongs don gsang ba 'di gsal
NK034(ngi)004:870: ba'i shes rab mdzod kyi sgo phye la dri ma
NK034(ngi)004:871: med pa'i rig pa rtogs pas zad mi shes pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:872: lta ba 'khor 'das gnyis su med par 'dres pas
NK034(ngi)004:873: nor bu rnyed pa 'dra bas yid bzhin nor 'dra'i
NK034(ngi)004:874: don 'di rtogs par gyis 'khor 'das gnyis bsre ba'i
NK034(ngi)004:875: gdams ngag gi spyod pa la dor ba bstan gsal
NK034(ngi)004:876: ba'i ye shes zang thal gyis 'khor 'das gnyis kyi
NK034(ngi)004:877: mtshams su thob cig rig pa ka dag gi ye
NK034(ngi)004:878: shes dri mas ma bsgribs par 'khor 'das gang gi
NK034(ngi)004:879: ngo bor yang ma grub pa'i nyams 'char de'i tshe
NK034(ngi)004:880: snang ba la byan tshud pa'o 7 yul sems gnyis
NK034(ngi)004:881: bsre ba'i gzer gyis sgom pa la dor ba bstan
NK034(ngi)004:882: sgron ma rang snang gi gzer gyis yul sems gnyis
NK034(ngi)004:883: kyi bar du thob cig sgron ma nyid 'byung ba'i
NK034(ngi)004:884: skyon dang bral bas mig gi yul du 'od dang
NK034(ngi)004:885: thig le du ma 'char ro mi 'dod kyang sku
NK034(ngi)004:886: sna tshogs pa yang 'char ro de ni ye shes
NK034(ngi)004:887: la byan tshud pa ces bya'o blo dngos gnyis bsre
NK034(ngi)004:888: ba'i gzer gyis lta ba la dor ba bstan ngo
NK034(ngi)004:889: bo rang dag gi gzer blo dngos gnyis kyi bar
NK034(ngi)004:890: du thob cig rig pa'i rtsal sna tshogs su shar
NK034(ngi)004:891: yang dri ma med par ye nas yod pas rtsol
NK034(ngi)004:892: bcas ma yin pa'i nyams mi 'dod kyang 'char te
NK034(ngi)004:893: stong nyid la byan tshud pa'o 7 yin min gnyis
NK034(ngi)004:894: bsre ba'i man ngag gis yin tshul la dor ba
NK034(ngi)004:895: bstan pa lta ba grol yan gyis gzer rtag chad
NK034(ngi)004:896: gnyis kyi bar du thob cig rang byung gi ye
NK034(ngi)004:897: shes de ye gdod ma nas 'khor 'das thams cad
NK034(ngi)004:898: yin par 'dug pa'i nyams 'char te bzang ngan gnyis
NK034(ngi)004:899: med du byan tshud pa'o 7 chos can chos nyid
NK034(ngi)004:900: bsre ba'i man ngag gis nyams myong la dor bar
NK034(ngi)004:901: bstan pa rig pa chos min gyi gzer chos can
NK034(ngi)004:902: chos nyid kyi bar du thob cig bya byed dang
NK034(ngi)004:903: bral ba rig pa'i ye shes ye gdod ma nas
NK034(ngi)004:904: yin par shes pa'i nyams mi 'dod kyang 'char te
NK034(ngi)004:905: de'i tshe chos nyid spros bral byan tshud pa'o 7
NK034(ngi)004:906: bying rgod gnyis bsre ba'i man ngag gis dgongs pa
NK034(ngi)004:907: la dor ba bstan sgo lnga rgya yan gyi gzer
NK034(ngi)004:908: bying rgod gnyis kyi bar la thob cig chags zhen
NK034(ngi)004:909: med pa sgo lnga rang yan gyi ye shes ye
NK034(ngi)004:910: nas rtsol sgrub las 'das pa'i nyams mi 'dod kyang
NK034(ngi)004:911: 'char ro de'i tshe dbang po la byan tshud pa'o
NK034(ngi)004:912: snang stong gnyis bsre ba'i man ngag gis 'bras bu
NK034(ngi)004:913: la dor ba bstan chos sku ye rdzogs kyi gzer
NK034(ngi)004:914: snang stong gnyis kyi bar la thob cig de ltar
NK034(ngi)004:915: snang zhing srid pa thams cad ye nas rang gi
NK034(ngi)004:916: rig pa la gzhan rtsol bcas yin par shes pas
NK034(ngi)004:917: 'di nyid la rtogs rgyu gang yang med pa'i nyams
NK034(ngi)004:918: 'char te rtogs tshad la byan tshud pa'o +thii gsal
NK034(ngi)004:919: ba rang ngos ma bsgribs pa shes rab rang grol
NK034(ngi)004:920: gzhan ngo la bzhag pa ni rtsa dang me phrad
NK034(ngi)004:921: pa lta bu'o 'khor 'das gnyis med du 'dres pas
NK034(ngi)004:922: rkyen gzhan la rag ma lus par thag chod dran
NK034(ngi)004:923: bsam ji ltar 'dug kyang rang snang yin pas snang
NK034(ngi)004:924: ba la dbang bsgyur nus pa'i rtags rnyed pa'o snang
NK034(ngi)004:925: ba cer grol du shes dran bsam la byan tshud
NK034(ngi)004:926: pa ni mun khang dang snang ba phrad pa lta
NK034(ngi)004:927: bu'o yul sems gnyis 'dres pa'i rkyen gyis rkyen nyid
NK034(ngi)004:928: skye med du grol bar thag chod 'gyu byed rang
NK034(ngi)004:929: sar dengs pas ye shes la dbang bsgyur nus pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:930: rtags rnyed pa'o rig pa ye dag gi dgongs pa
NK034(ngi)004:931: bzhi mngon du shes pa ni blo dngos gnyis 'dres
NK034(ngi)004:932: pas rig pa la ye nas bar mtshams med par
NK034(ngi)004:933: thag chod bya dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs shes
NK034(ngi)004:934: pas stong nyid la dbang bsgyur nus pa'i rtags rnyed
NK034(ngi)004:935: pa'o yid mthun pa'i pho mo phrad pa lta bu'o
NK034(ngi)004:936: 'dod chags kyi dub pa yod pa skye ba ltar
NK034(ngi)004:937: shes pa gzhi thog tu zang thal lo rang ngo
NK034(ngi)004:938: phyogs bral gyi ye shes rang rkyen du shar bas
NK034(ngi)004:939: yin min gyi rtsis las 'das pa ni yin min
NK034(ngi)004:940: gnyis 'dres pas phyogs med kyi shes pa yul med
NK034(ngi)004:941: du shar bar thag chod dran rtog gi rtsis gdab
NK034(ngi)004:942: las 'das pas bzang ngan gnyis su med par dbang
NK034(ngi)004:943: bsgyur nus pa'i rtags rnyed pa'o bzhin dang me long
NK034(ngi)004:944: phrad pa me long la bzhin bstan pas rang ngo
NK034(ngi)004:945: shes pa ltar dngos po rang thog tu grol ba
NK034(ngi)004:946: zang thal lo lta bu'o lta sgom las grol ba'i
NK034(ngi)004:947: rtog pa sna tshogs rol par shar bas chos can
NK034(ngi)004:948: chos nyid gnyis 'dres pas 'bad rtsol dang bral bar
NK034(ngi)004:949: thag chod cir snang rig pa'i snang bar shes pas
NK034(ngi)004:950: chos nyid la dbang bsgyur nus pa'i rtags rnyed pa'o
NK034(ngi)004:951: ba mo la nyi ma reg pa rang zhu ba
NK034(ngi)004:952: dang 'dra bar nyon mongs pa chos nyid du zang
NK034(ngi)004:953: thal lo lta bu'o snang srid sor bzhag gi dgongs
NK034(ngi)004:954: pa ye rgyas btab pas yul rkyen mnyam pa nyid
NK034(ngi)004:955: du shes pa ni bying rgod gnyis med du 'dres
NK034(ngi)004:956: pas snang srid 'di dag rang bzhag tu thag chod
NK034(ngi)004:957: tshogs drug gi shes pa mnyam gzhag tu shes pas
NK034(ngi)004:958: rtogs tshad la dbang bsgyur nus pa'i rtags rnyed pa'o
NK034(ngi)004:959: bu gcig po dang phrad pa lta bu'o rtogs dang
NK034(ngi)004:960: bral ba 'dra bar cir snang 'bras bu ye rdzogs
NK034(ngi)004:961: su zang thal lo chos sku 'bad rtsol med par
NK034(ngi)004:962: ye nas rang dang 'du 'bral med pa yin pas
NK034(ngi)004:963: snod bcud rang sar grol ba ni dbul snang stong
NK034(ngi)004:964: gnyis su med pas rig pa'i ye shes kyi ngo
NK034(ngi)004:965: bo rtsol sgrub la ma ltos par bud+d+ha bar thag
NK034(ngi)004:966: chod rig pa rang dag gi lta bas cir snang
NK034(ngi)004:967: 'bras bur grol bas dgongs pa la dbang bsgyur nus
NK034(ngi)004:968: pa'i rtags rnyed pa'o po gter mdzod dang phrad pa
NK034(ngi)004:969: dbul ba dang bral ba ltar cir snang 'bras bu
NK034(ngi)004:970: ye rdzogs su zang thal lo lta bu'o +thii sh+ri
NK034(ngi)004:971: sing+ha dgongs pa yongs su mya ngan las 'das pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:972: tshe 'od zer gyi phung po dang bcas te nam
NK034(ngi)004:973: mkha' la gshegs pas ye shes mdo brgyal bkra shis
NK034(ngi)004:974: khri sgo na bzhugs pa'i dus zhing sa la 'gyel
NK034(ngi)004:975: bar gyur te kye ma kyi hud kyi sgra bsgrags
NK034(ngi)004:976: pas nam mkha' la sgra chen po grags te gsang
NK034(ngi)004:977: ba'i yi ge rnams bkra shis khri sgo'i ka ba'i
NK034(ngi)004:978: bsam len yod kyi longs la dur khrod b+ha sing
NK034(ngi)004:979: du song bya ba byung ngo de nyid brgyal sangs
NK034(ngi)004:980: nas bltas pas 'od kyi dkyil nas phyag g.yas pa
NK034(ngi)004:981: phyungs te ye shes mdo brgyal ba las bslang ba'i
NK034(ngi)004:982: don du rin po che'i za ma tog sen gang
NK034(ngi)004:983: ba gcig phyag mthil du babs so de nyid babs
NK034(ngi)004:984: pa tsam gyis rtogs pa gdengs dang ldan par gyur
NK034(ngi)004:985: to bkra shis khri sgor babs pa sh+r+ai sing ha'i
NK034(ngi)004:986: zhal chems gzer bu bdun pa long ba'i sna khrid
NK034(ngi)004:987: dang 'dra ba rdzogs so ye shes mdo'i bzhag thabs
NK034(ngi)004:988: bzhi yod sarba e ka ra chos thams cad stong
NK034(ngi)004:989: pa ye shes kyi thabs yin stong pa gzhi ye
NK034(ngi)004:990: 'byung ba dag ngang la phyag 'tshal lo gsang phyi
NK034(ngi)004:991: nang gi don sngags gsang ba'i mdo don 'dir snang
NK034(ngi)004:992: ba dus gsum bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi thugs kyi
NK034(ngi)004:993: dgongs shar ba blo yi mun sel sgron ma 'od
NK034(ngi)004:994: po che 'jig rten ma rig pa rab rib rnams
NK034(ngi)004:995: ni bsal bya'i phyir rang rig lu gu rgyud ye
NK034(ngi)004:996: shes kyi kha dog kun gyis rtogs dka' kun spangs
NK034(ngi)004:997: pa 'gyur lta ba med thabs kyis man ngag gis
NK034(ngi)004:998: rgya yis bzung byas te rgya che rab zab rnam
NK034(ngi)004:999: dag sgron ma'i dbyings su bcug nas kyang mtha' rtag
NK034(ngi)004:1000: chad kyi bral nyag thig le gcig ngang du gzhag
NK034(ngi)004:1001: par bya'o brgyal bi ma la mi tra ba rnams
NK034(ngi)004:1002: ni gdams ngag 'di yis dbugs phyungs te sangs rgyas
NK034(ngi)004:1003: rnams kyi dgongs pa dang mnyam pa nyid du grags
NK034(ngi)004:1004: gang zhig bzung bas ma zin rig pa de rang
NK034(ngi)004:1005: snang de nyid ci nas 'dzin 'dod skal ldan blo
NK034(ngi)004:1006: che ba yi ye shes mdo'i zhal chems ge 'di
NK034(ngi)004:1007: la rtag tu goms par gyis e ma hoh ngo
NK034(ngi)004:1008: mtshar 'di la rtag tu goms par byas nyams su
NK034(ngi)004:1009: blangs gzhi na bde ba shugs la 'byung kye ma
NK034(ngi)004:1010: mnyam pa chen mi g.yo ba'i ting nge 'dzin po'i
NK034(ngi)004:1011: sa thob par 'dod na de nyid la nyin mtshan
NK034(ngi)004:1012: rtag tu ma yengs pa goms par gyis shig spyod
NK034(ngi)004:1013: pa thams cad la rtsal sbyong bar 'dod na snang
NK034(ngi)004:1014: ba cer bzhag tu 'byung ba rang dag snang ba
NK034(ngi)004:1015: thams cad zhog cig sgom pa gtsor byed pa'i man
NK034(ngi)004:1016: ngag thams cad la stobs rnyed par 'dod na rgya
NK034(ngi)004:1017: mtsho cog bzhag gi dgongs pas blo rgyun chad 'khrul
NK034(ngi)004:1018: ma 'khrul dngos gnyis gcig tu dril la zhog cig
NK034(ngi)004:1019: lta ba thams cad las rang grol bar 'dod na
NK034(ngi)004:1020: ri bo cog bzhag gi lta snang ba rang snang
NK034(ngi)004:1021: bas chos thams cad zad sar skyol zhig sku gsum
NK034(ngi)004:1022: bzhi bzhag 'bras bu thams cad rang sar gnas par
NK034(ngi)004:1023: 'dod na rig pa cog gzhag gi lta bas man
NK034(ngi)004:1024: ngag la 'khrul pa thams cad rang sar grol bar
NK034(ngi)004:1025: zhog cig snang 'khrul pa'i ba rang gzhag yin pas
NK034(ngi)004:1026: ye nas stong pa dang 'brel ba dang blo rang
NK034(ngi)004:1027: sar bzhag pas ye nas dngos po dang 'brel ba
NK034(ngi)004:1028: dang chos rnams rang sar bzhag pas nang gi 'bras
NK034(ngi)004:1029: bu dang snang ba rang lugs su dbyings dang rig
NK034(ngi)004:1030: dang thabs lam 'das pa'i 'brel ba dang 'khrul pa
NK034(ngi)004:1031: 'bras bu rang dag yin thams cad cog bzhag yin
NK034(ngi)004:1032: pas ye nas rang grol dang 'brel ba'o wal snang
NK034(ngi)004:1033: ba 'di po rjes med chu'i ri mo lta bus
NK034(ngi)004:1034: snang ba gcig thog tu gcig ngo bo'i gzhag dran
NK034(ngi)004:1035: pa rjes med mkha' la bya 'phur lta bus bsam
NK034(ngi)004:1036: pa gcig thog tu gcig bzhag pa bsam pa rnam
NK034(ngi)004:1037: par dag pa dang 'khrul pa rang dag mkha' 'gro
NK034(ngi)004:1038: rnyi las bton pa lta bus stong pa gcig thog
NK034(ngi)004:1039: tu gcig bzhag pa dang dag pa ldog med rims
NK034(ngi)004:1040: nad byang ba lta bus rig pa gcig thog tu
NK034(ngi)004:1041: gcig grol ba'o +thii snang ba spyod cing bsgyur nus
NK034(ngi)004:1042: pa chang dang ra ro ba lta bus 'byung ba
NK034(ngi)004:1043: lnga rang sar bzhag pa dang sems gnas shing tshad
NK034(ngi)004:1044: zin pa rngon pas ri dwags rgyal zin pa bzung
NK034(ngi)004:1045: ba lta bus sems rang sar snang ba la byan
NK034(ngi)004:1046: tshud pa gzhag pa dang chos la mi gnas pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:1047: shes pas zad sar skyel ba rig pa mthong ba
NK034(ngi)004:1048: bzhin dang me long lta bus chos thams cad rang
NK034(ngi)004:1049: sar bzhag pa dang 'khrul pa ma thog tu grol
NK034(ngi)004:1050: ba sbrul dang mdud pa lta bus rang gi rang
NK034(ngi)004:1051: grol 'khrul dang ma 'khrul med pa rang sar bzhag
NK034(ngi)004:1052: pa'o snang ba rang grol ba gzu po'i blo can
NK034(ngi)004:1053: lha khang du phyin pa lta snang ba la blo
NK034(ngi)004:1054: ma zhen pa / bu'o bsam pa thams cad gzhi
NK034(ngi)004:1055: la thim pas rgya mtsho rlung gis bskyod pa lta
NK034(ngi)004:1056: bu'o dbyings dang rig pa rang phrad pa ri rgyal
NK034(ngi)004:1057: gyi rtse mor phyin pa lta bu'o sku gsum phyir
NK034(ngi)004:1058: mi ldog pa rang sa la sleb pa ni bse
NK034(ngi)004:1059: shing gi 'bras bu lta bu'o rgyur mi ldog lta
NK034(ngi)004:1060: sgom spyod pa'i srog shing yin rengs pa snang ba
NK034(ngi)004:1061: rtsal sgyur rnams kyi gnya' gcod yin stor ba nyin
NK034(ngi)004:1062: mtshan kha sbyor rnams kyi rjes gcod yin ltebs pa
NK034(ngi)004:1063: lta ba grong khyer rgyun gcod rnams kyi rgyangs shing
NK034(ngi)004:1064: yin rgya che snang ba spar gyis bzung ba'i man
NK034(ngi)004:1065: ngag dmu sems rgod thur srab 'jug pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)004:1066: rno la reg pa ngar gyis 'dogs pa'i man ngag
NK034(ngi)004:1067: byas pa rtogs tshad thams cad rang sar bzhag pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:1068: man ngag go +thii sna snang ba tshogs lam du
NK034(ngi)004:1069: khyer ba'i rkang dran pa sems zad pa'i sa rgyun
NK034(ngi)004:1070: thag gcod pa'i lag rig dbyings pa dngos la lta
NK034(ngi)004:1071: ba'i mig 'khrul pa gzhi la de nyid ngang du
NK034(ngi)004:1072: dag pa'i khrus so snang ba 'khrul snang ral grol
NK034(ngi)004:1073: thug phrad kyi lam rig pa sems thug phrad kyi
NK034(ngi)004:1074: gzhi mthong ba rig pa thug phrad kyi yul grol
NK034(ngi)004:1075: ba chos las 'das pa thug phrad kyi 'bras bu'o
NK034(ngi)004:1076: dz+ny+aa na s+au tra dgongs pa yongs su mya ngan
NK034(ngi)004:1077: las 'da' ba'i tshe bi ma la mi tra brgyal
NK034(ngi)004:1078: zhing sa la 'gyel te kye ma kyi hud kyi
NK034(ngi)004:1079: sgra chen po 'don zhing gnas pa las nam mkha'
NK034(ngi)004:1080: 'od phung gi dkyil nas sgra chen po grags te
NK034(ngi)004:1081: brgyal sangs nas bstas pas phyag g.yas pa'i gru mo
NK034(ngi)004:1082: man chad phyungs te bi ma la mi tra'i phyag
NK034(ngi)004:1083: g.yas pa'i mthil du rin po che'i za ma tog
NK034(ngi)004:1084: sen gang ba gcig babs so de zhal phye nas
NK034(ngi)004:1085: gzigs pas bee d+aur+ya mthing kas rang nan du rin
NK034(ngi)004:1086: po che lnga'i shog gu la bris pa gcig bzhugs
NK034(ngi)004:1087: 'dug ste bi ma las bltas pa tsam gyis rtogs
NK034(ngi)004:1088: pa'i gdeng dang ldan par gyur to dur khrod chen
NK034(ngi)004:1089: po b+ha sing du snang bar byas pa ye shes
NK034(ngi)004:1090: mdo'i zhal chems bzhag thabs bzhis rten gcig la sangs
NK034(ngi)004:1091: rgya bar byed pa mun khung gi sgron me dang
NK034(ngi)004:1092: 'dra ba rdzogs so spyod pa rang bzhag sgom pa
NK034(ngi)004:1093: rang bzhag lta ba rang bzhag 'bras bu rang bzhag
NK034(ngi)004:1094: gi gdams ngag go s+aa m+aa y+aa amtha&a&a&a shu b+ham
NK034(ngi)004:1095: gser yig canthem med mkhas pa bye ma la'i zhal
NK034(ngi)004:1096: chems bzhugs so rang rig gsal ba'i sgron ma ni
NK034(ngi)004:1097: rtogs pa'i shes rab phyag btsal nas sems can sangs
NK034(ngi)004:1098: rgyas sa la 'god yun du bsags pa'i sgrib pa
NK034(ngi)004:1099: 'thug po yang tshig gsum gnad du brdeg pas shel
NK034(ngi)004:1100: sgong phyes pa 'dra skye med ka dag bsgrub pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:1101: mtha' sku gsum lhun grub 'bras bu'i lam dgongs pa
NK034(ngi)004:1102: nyag gcig sgron mar gsal dbyings rig rnam par dag
NK034(ngi)004:1103: pa'i sgron ma yis lta ba gsal byed sgron ma
NK034(ngi)004:1104: bstan gsal sdud pa las byed sgron ma chos mchog
NK034(ngi)004:1105: smra ba mi 'khrugs yin 'gro ba'i mtshan brjod las
NK034(ngi)004:1106: mar me ye shes sgron zhes pa'o lta ba gsal
NK034(ngi)004:1107: byed dbang po'i sgo ru shar zhes pa'o stong gsal
NK034(ngi)004:1108: thig le'i sgron ma yis 'khrul snang rgya yis 'debs
NK034(ngi)004:1109: par bstan mtshan brjod las ye shes snang ba lam
NK034(ngi)004:1110: me ba zhes pa'o shes rab rang byung sgron ma
NK034(ngi)004:1111: yis rtog pa gdeng du tshud par bstan shes rab
NK034(ngi)004:1112: chen pos skad cig la chos kun khong du chud
NK034(ngi)004:1113: pa po rgyang zhags chu yi sgron ma yis rig
NK034(ngi)004:1114: pa lan gsum gnad du bzung snang dang stong dang
NK034(ngi)004:1115: gsal dang sgron ma chos kyi mchog ces so rig
NK034(ngi)004:1116: pa'i lam gnas sems dang ye shes dbye rig pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:1117: ngo bo nges tshig gnas la 'char sgo las des
NK034(ngi)004:1118: yul chos 'bras bu yon tan phyogs tshad dbye ba'i
NK034(ngi)004:1119: dus sems kyis tshes bco lnga chos su dbye ba'o
NK034(ngi)004:1120: ngo bo gnas dang lam dang bsgo skyon dang yon
NK034(ngi)004:1121: tan snang tshul gyis don gsum the tshom med pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:1122: blo dpe don rtogs zhes 'bras bu'i gsang lam kun
NK034(ngi)004:1123: gzhi me long lta bu'i ye shes bskal ba gsum
NK034(ngi)004:1124: gtsug gi rgyud las chos skur dbye kun gzhi sna
NK034(ngi)004:1125: tshogs bsags pa'i kun gzhi kun gyi gzhi yin kyang
NK034(ngi)004:1126: rnam par byang ba'i rten ma yin zhes so ye
NK034(ngi)004:1127: shes mthong lam 'byung ba'i dwangs snyigs dbye 'khrul rig
NK034(ngi)004:1128: pa chos min gyi gnyis mi gnas par shar /
NK034(ngi)004:1130: dag pa'i snang ba dang chos nyid kyi snang ba
NK034(ngi)004:1131: snang ba gsum sbyor rang 'byung sa la sbyor dag
NK034(ngi)004:1132: snang phyed pas lam rtags tshad kyang zin zhes so
NK034(ngi)004:1133: dbye ba gsum gyi rig pa rkyen rkyen med kyi
NK034(ngi)004:1134: shes pa rang dag dang phrol mig gi rig pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:1135: 'char sgo dbang pos rig pa gcer thon pa chos
NK034(ngi)004:1136: rkyen dag pa yin pas rkyen ma 'khrul na rig
NK034(ngi)004:1137: pa rtog med zang thal chos nyid chos sku spros
NK034(ngi)004:1138: dang bral sku zang thal de bzhin nyid kyi don
NK034(ngi)004:1139: mig 'bum las gis de bzhin nyid shes na chos
NK034(ngi)004:1140: thams cad kyi mdo dang rgyas pa shes par 'gyur
NK034(ngi)004:1141: ro zhes pa'o de ka na rang byed pa med
NK034(ngi)004:1142: pa byung gi ye shes chen po rang shar bas
NK034(ngi)004:1143: ye shes mtshan brjod las snang ba lam me ba
NK034(ngi)004:1144: zhes pas so de ka sems mi gnas par rig
NK034(ngi)004:1145: pa dngos su shar ba can kun gyi sna 'khrid
NK034(ngi)004:1146: par shes pas 'gro ba'i mar me ye shes sgron
NK034(ngi)004:1147: de ka mig na phar mkhyen pa ma 'gags par
NK034(ngi)004:1148: shar bas ye shes mig gcig dri ma med dri
NK034(ngi)004:1149: ma gsum bral ces pa'o mig gi dbang po mthong
NK034(ngi)004:1150: ba ma 'gags par rtog med kyi ye shes rang
NK034(ngi)004:1151: gsal ba ni rig pa mngon sum dbang po'i bstan
NK034(ngi)004:1152: pa ste mngon sum mthong ba'i mig ces de la
NK034(ngi)004:1153: bya de ka na sangs rgyas kyi thugs yang dag
NK034(ngi)004:1154: pa'i ye zhes yin pas sangs rgyas kun gyi khyung
NK034(ngi)004:1155: rol pa las thugs mchog ni 'gro ba kun gyis
NK034(ngi)004:1156: spyan la shar zhes pa'o de ka sems can kun
NK034(ngi)004:1157: gyi sna 'khrid par shar bas rig sdud pa las
NK034(ngi)004:1158: pa khyim du mi gnas lam la mkhas par 'gyur
NK034(ngi)004:1159: zhes pa'o mi gnas phar shar ba'i rig pa rang
NK034(ngi)004:1160: ngo ma shes na ma rig pa de la zer
NK034(ngi)004:1161: dmigs bu med pas rig pa'ang ngo ma shes na
NK034(ngi)004:1162: rgyu 'khor ba las mi thar byang chub reg par
NK034(ngi)004:1163: nus ma yin zhes pa'o mig lta bar ngo ma
NK034(ngi)004:1164: shes ma rtogs pa'i sems can thams cad na dmus
NK034(ngi)004:1165: long sdud pa las dmigs bu med pa bye ba
NK034(ngi)004:1166: khrag khrig rnams lam yang mi shes grong khyer 'jug
NK034(ngi)004:1167: par ga la 'gyur zhes dang ma rig 'khrul 'khor
NK034(ngi)004:1168: 'di la zad med 'phel ba med ces so yid
NK034(ngi)004:1169: spyod kyis spyo 'jal gyi rnam pa sems gtan la
NK034(ngi)004:1170: 'bebs pa ni 'dongs pa nam mkha' nam mkha' che
NK034(ngi)004:1171: las snyeg pa 'dra zhes pa'o nyams su myong sku
NK034(ngi)004:1172: gsum rang gi sna khrid par 'char ba ni mig
NK034(ngi)004:1173: gi dbang po mthong ba ma blo yul du bya
NK034(ngi)004:1174: ba las don rang gi mtshan nyid du 'gags pa
NK034(ngi)004:1175: rig pa chos kyi sku mthong ba nges par mkhyen
NK034(ngi)004:1176: pa shes rab longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o mig gi
NK034(ngi)004:1177: de kho na nyid snying po ye shes kyi lus
NK034(ngi)004:1178: can ni sprul pa'i sku ste sku gsum 'du 'bral
NK034(ngi)004:1179: med chos sku par rang gi sna khrid par shar
NK034(ngi)004:1180: bas mchog gi mtshan brjod las dang po sku gsum
NK034(ngi)004:1181: 'chang zhes pa'o de dpe shel don rtags gsum gyi
NK034(ngi)004:1182: gyi ye shes gtan la phebs pas don gsum the
NK034(ngi)004:1183: ngo shes yid ches thag chod pa tshom med pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:1184: blo zhes pa'o don gyi ye shes chos sku zang
NK034(ngi)004:1185: thal rtog med ngo shes pas kun don yon tan
NK034(ngi)004:1186: gsum 'gro ba kun gyi snying po yin gyi bdag
NK034(ngi)004:1187: ces pa'o don gsum rig phung po lnga ni nang
NK034(ngi)004:1188: du rig pa ngos bzung ba ni mig ma 'gul
NK034(ngi)004:1189: chos sku ka dag spros bral yin bar nam mkha'
NK034(ngi)004:1190: sprin bral gyi klong du gtad pas dbyings rnam par
NK034(ngi)004:1191: dag pa'i ye shes kyi spyan rnam par dag pa
NK034(ngi)004:1192: sgron mar gsal te rdo rje lu gu rgyud snang
NK034(ngi)004:1193: ba'i nyams gong du 'phel ba kyi sku ye shes
NK034(ngi)004:1194: zang thal chen po'i dgongs pa ste cog bzhag chen
NK034(ngi)004:1195: po bzhi'i yi ge med par shes par bya ngang
NK034(ngi)004:1196: la bzhag go rig pa tshad la dngos med kyi
NK034(ngi)004:1197: rig pa dngos ltar snang ba phebs shing mngon sum
NK034(ngi)004:1198: gyis snang ba'o rig pa lam nyams kyi lugs rtags
NK034(ngi)004:1199: kyi snang ba ni mig 'char sgo gi 'bras man
NK034(ngi)004:1200: shel bu gsal byed kyi me long gong mi drag
NK034(ngi)004:1201: mnan pas snang ba 'char lugs thugs rje 'od zer
NK034(ngi)004:1202: gyi snang ba shar te 'greng bu dang phyed nyal
NK034(ngi)004:1203: zlum 'khyil thig le dang thig zhing khams phran longs
NK034(ngi)004:1204: sku dang sprul rigs drug sku'i snang ba 'char ro
NK034(ngi)004:1205: spyan lnga yang rim pas nyams su blangs pas spyan
NK034(ngi)004:1206: lnga chags pa med par 'char zhes pa'o skye med
NK034(ngi)004:1207: dbyings dang rig par dbyer mi phyed kyi klong du
NK034(ngi)004:1208: 'gag med kyi rig pa rang grol bas chos ka
NK034(ngi)004:1209: dag pa chen po'i bdag nyid rnams thams cad zad
NK034(ngi)004:1210: sar skyel ba'o ngo bo ka spros bral dag rang
NK034(ngi)004:1211: bzhin lhun grub rgya ma chad thun mong ma yin
NK034(ngi)004:1212: pa'i gnyug ma la lhun grub kyi rol ba 'gag
NK034(ngi)004:1213: med pa'o mtha' bral phyogs ris med pa lta ba'i
NK034(ngi)004:1214: mtha' brgyad dang bral ba'o gdeng dmigs pa gtang bzhag
NK034(ngi)004:1215: med pa bsgom gol sar ma lhung ba pa'i gdeng
NK034(ngi)004:1216: zhe 'dod nyam nga glang po che lta bu med
NK034(ngi)004:1217: pa spyod pa'i gdeng spangs thob re dogs med pa
NK034(ngi)004:1218: 'bras bu'i gdeng lam gsum gdeng bzhi gnad kyi man
NK034(ngi)004:1219: ngag yin lung rgyal ba'i sgra tshad bstan bcos lung
NK034(ngi)004:1220: rig gis dbab tu med dang rig pa man ngag
NK034(ngi)004:1221: gsum yid bla ma'i gdams ngag las ches gdams pa
NK034(ngi)004:1222: gnad la phob gol yang dag pa'i lta ba mi
NK034(ngi)004:1223: thob sar ltung bas lta sgom shes par byos sna
NK034(ngi)004:1224: tshogs mu stegs blo bzung gi lta ba a nu
NK034(ngi)004:1225: man chad bya byed 'bad rtsol gyi gol sa yin
NK034(ngi)004:1226: lhun grub stong rdzong khyab che la don phyal pa
NK034(ngi)004:1227: ma rig lhun gyis grub pas 'khrul pa'i gol sa
NK034(ngi)004:1228: yin mtha' bral brjod med stong pa'i khas mi len
NK034(ngi)004:1229: pas chad pas mthar ltung la bzla ste chad pa
NK034(ngi)004:1230: mtha' zad lta ba yin sgyu 'phrul 'od snying gi
NK034(ngi)004:1231: dkyil na 'od dang 'od kyi gong bur yod zer
NK034(ngi)004:1232: ba gang zag gi bdag tu 'gro gsal bdag 'dzin
NK034(ngi)004:1233: pa rtag par lta dang mtshungs pa ste de dag
NK034(ngi)004:1234: lta ba'i gol sar shes par gyis stong pa had
NK034(ngi)004:1235: po'i lta shin tu spyod nas stong pa sgom dang
NK034(ngi)004:1236: mi rtog ltengs me re ba po'i sems 'dzin dang
NK034(ngi)004:1237: btang rtog sgom snyoms ltengs po'i mun sgom dang ma
NK034(ngi)004:1238: tshor nyan thos yid byed 'gog pa dang bde ba
NK034(ngi)004:1239: skye bde stong rtsol bcas med lus sbyangs dang yid
NK034(ngi)004:1240: 'gyur gcod pa'i dbugs rtsol sgrub byas chos yin pas
NK034(ngi)004:1241: 'dzin rlung sgom rnams 'di rnams sgom pa'i bsgoms kyang
