NK034(ngi)004:1242: sangs mi rgya'o gol sar shes par gyis blang dor
NK034(ngi)004:1243: gcig spang gcig bsgrub pa bdag tu rtog pa'i spyod
NK034(ngi)004:1244: pa dang rtsol sgrub dge sbyong ngam tshul 'chos byed
NK034(ngi)004:1245: pa'i spyod pa dang brtul zhugs ci dga' dga' byed
NK034(ngi)004:1246: pa smyon par byed pa'i spyod pa dang 'di rnams
NK034(ngi)004:1247: rang bzhin brtul zhugs med pa spyod pa'i gol sar
NK034(ngi)004:1248: shes par gyis rgyu rkyen zad pa'i chad pa phyogs
NK034(ngi)004:1249: mtshams kyi gol sa stong 'jam dang du ma ro
NK034(ngi)004:1250: rdzogs pa chen po nyag gcig yin zer ba de'i
NK034(ngi)004:1251: rig byed gsar bar smra ba'i gol sa'o gcig thig
NK034(ngi)004:1252: le chen po'i ngang grol dang sku gsum lhun 'bras
NK034(ngi)004:1253: bu min skye mched mu bzhi'i 'bras bu'o grub lam
NK034(ngi)004:1254: snang 'dod pa rnams 'bras bu re dogs kyi gol
NK034(ngi)004:1255: sa thob rgyu yod zer ba yin snang la rang
NK034(ngi)004:1256: sa'i der yang ma grub ste stong la ngo bo
NK034(ngi)004:1257: ka dag mtha' grol gyi lta ba bzhin med pa
NK034(ngi)004:1258: chos nyid nam mkha' lta ba'i mchog gsal la rtog
NK034(ngi)004:1259: pa med pa ngo bo ka dag stong pa la
NK034(ngi)004:1260: phyogs ma chad mkhyen pa la mi spyod rang ngo
NK034(ngi)004:1261: la mi 'gag 'bras bu'i mchog thim pa la mi
NK034(ngi)004:1262: rmugs dgongs pa thams cad dbyer mi phyed pa'o cir
NK034(ngi)004:1263: snang bkag pa med pas ngo bo stong gsal chen
NK034(ngi)004:1264: po phyogs gar yang ma lhung mtshan ma rang sar
NK034(ngi)004:1265: grol lo rang bzhin rgya ma chad de spyod pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:1266: mchog mthong rtog sgyu ma'i rang bzhin med pa'i yin
NK034(ngi)004:1267: pas ci rnam par rtog pa cir blo yin pas
NK034(ngi)004:1268: bsam bsam rgyu med pa pa kun brjod pa dang
NK034(ngi)004:1269: bral ba spangs ye shes me chen g.yo de'i ngang
NK034(ngi)004:1270: las rang bzhin ma bskyod lhan ne zhog lhan ne
NK034(ngi)004:1271: lhang nge tshogs drug lhug pa dbang po rgya yan
NK034(ngi)004:1272: khog thong thong la grong chod la thong bzhag na
NK034(ngi)004:1273: mnyam bzhag chen po yin te don de sgom pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:1274: mchog mchog dmigs gtad med pa rnams rnal ma rang
NK034(ngi)004:1275: so gnyug ma gzhi gdeng bzhi khyer na grub mtha'
NK034(ngi)004:1276: ngan pa'i lta ba chod phyin bsgrod med par slebs
NK034(ngi)004:1277: pas byang chub sems kyi sgron ma ngos zin na
NK034(ngi)004:1278: kun tu 'od kyi sa non sa gcig pa rkang
NK034(ngi)004:1279: med mkha' sgron ma rnam par dag pa bzhag la
NK034(ngi)004:1280: 'gro na lta ba'i nam mkha' rnam par dag pa'i
NK034(ngi)004:1281: nang du rgyab sha chod grogs med gcig pur 'dug
NK034(ngi)004:1282: na sgom pa'i rgyab sha chod rig pa thig le
NK034(ngi)004:1283: nyag gcig la bar mtshams med lta med sku la
NK034(ngi)004:1284: bltas pas 'di'i phyi nang 'di yin bya ba med
NK034(ngi)004:1285: 'bras bu'i rgyab sha chod bdag ni bye ma la
NK034(ngi)004:1286: thos chung blo zhen ma yin te sgra tshad bstan
NK034(ngi)004:1287: bcos grub mtha' sogs sde snod gsum 'dul ba mdo
NK034(ngi)004:1288: sde mngon pa gyi don go longs rgyud sde bzhi
NK034(ngi)004:1289: yi bya ba'i spyod pa'i rnal 'byor bla na med
NK034(ngi)004:1290: pa'i rgyud do khong don shig 'bum tsho drug rnams
NK034(ngi)004:1291: bzhugs pa'i a ti la bdag gis dgongs pa ma
NK034(ngi)004:1292: lon gcig kyang med khyad par sems sde rtsa gcig
NK034(ngi)004:1293: dang klong sde nyi shu rtsa gcig dang de rnams
NK034(ngi)004:1294: nang nas zab pa man ngag sde de dag man
NK034(ngi)004:1295: ngag snying bcud bdag gis shes de rnams nang na
NK034(ngi)004:1296: mar gyi yang zhun 'dra ba ni rdzogs pa chen
NK034(ngi)004:1297: po gser gyi nyi ma gsang ba bla na med
NK034(ngi)004:1298: pa'i skor rab tu snang byed thig le gsang ba'i
NK034(ngi)004:1299: mchog rgyud sde bco brgyad ti ka sa gcod bcas
NK034(ngi)004:1300: brgya dang bcu dgu'i zangs yig g.yu yig dung yig
NK034(ngi)004:1301: la sogs pa man ngag sde dang bcas de yi
NK034(ngi)004:1302: nang nas zab pa'i man ngag zhal thems brgyad po
NK034(ngi)004:1303: sangs rgyas la gsum rig 'dzin la lnga 'di sangs
NK034(ngi)004:1304: rgyas dus gsum gyi stong gi dgongs bcud dril nas
NK034(ngi)004:1305: ni bstan pa'i bu gcig bstan sangs rgyas pa la
NK034(ngi)004:1306: dgos pa'i pa'i btsas su bzhag bdag ni skye ba
NK034(ngi)004:1307: lnga brgya'i lus blangs shes rig pa'i gnas bco brgyad
NK034(ngi)004:1308: mkhyen pa'o rig 'dzin lnga ni rim gyis thob chos
NK034(ngi)004:1309: nyid zad sar skyol nas lhag med grol sems can
NK034(ngi)004:1310: don la dgongs nas 'pho ba chen po'i sku sangs
NK034(ngi)004:1311: rgyas stong gi bstan pa ma zhig bar sems can
NK034(ngi)004:1312: sangs rgyas sar bkod bdag gis spyod da lta bdag
NK034(ngi)004:1313: ni rtse lnga dag na phyin gang zag las dag
NK034(ngi)004:1314: seng ge dbang phyug khyod rgyu ni rin chen sna
NK034(ngi)004:1315: lnga'i byang bu la rin chen sna lngas yig bris
NK034(ngi)004:1316: pod chung gsum mchims phu'i dge gong brag la lcags
NK034(ngi)004:1317: kyi ga'ura gtems nas yod bstan pa'i bu gcig zhal
NK034(ngi)004:1318: thems gdams pa 'di khyod kyi snying la phur la
NK034(ngi)004:1319: nyams su longs rig 'dzin nyi shu rtsa gcig gdams
NK034(ngi)004:1320: pa dang dga' rab rdo rje'i zhal mjal dmas ngag
NK034(ngi)004:1321: yin sangs rgyas nyag gcig dgongs pa thun cig dang
NK034(ngi)004:1322: / gdams ngag tshig gcig ngang zhog bdag ni hor
NK034(ngi)004:1323: gyi yul byang phyogs sdig skyong rgyal po'i don dmyal
NK034(ngi)004:1324: bar skyes pa gcig 'don du la 'gro zhes gsungs
NK034(ngi)004:1325: spa gor gtsang lung dgon pa ru zhal chems phog
NK034(ngi)004:1326: nas mkha' la rlung ltar gshegs sa ma y+aa gu
NK034(ngi)004:1327: ru na mo e ka du na ra kan +thii
NK034(ngi)004:1328: sum re tshe dbang las dbang phyag rgya'i dbang lhun
NK034(ngi)004:1329: grub kyi dbang de rnams kyis rig 'dzin thob pa'o
NK034(ngi)004:1330: seng ge dbang phyug gis phyi gong rdza'i ra bar
